(4, 7, 'Tour Begins - Pickup from Hotel or Specified pick location', 'Your tour begins when we pick everybody up from the Greater Toronto Area (Mississauga, Brampton, Etobicoke, Oakville, etc) or from a Niagara Falls Hotel or specified pickup location in one of our meticulous maintained luxury vehicles, pick up time depends entirely on you!', 'Toronto, ON, Canada or Niagara Falls, ON, Canada', '8:30 - 9:30 am', '43.653226', '-79.38318429999998', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(5, 7, 'Arrive at Canadian side of Niagara Falls.', 'Your custom tour arrives at the main attraction, the majestic Canadian Niagara Falls.', 'Niagara Falls, ON, Canada', '11:00 am', '43.11763235889231', '-79.13438207656247', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(6, 7, 'Hornblower Niagara Cruise (Seasonal)', 'No waiting in line (VIP treatment) for the Niagara Falls boat tour called the HORNBLOWER NIAGARA CRUISES (seasonal).  If the Hornblower cruise is not available then you will experience either Journey Behind the Falls or enjoy the panoramic view of the Niagara Falls from the Skylon Tower.  ', 'Hornblower Niagara Cruises, Niagara Falls, ON, Canada', '11:15 am', '43.088677', '-79.0743622', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(7, 7, 'Explore Niagara Falls', 'Your free time begins now!  You can explore the Niagara Falls and surrounding areas on your own or with your group (or skip the exploration to save time on your tour).  You will be provided a free lanyard with your drivers contact information.  In the event you become lost, the driver is only a phone call away.  ', 'Niagara Falls, ON, Canada', '12:00 pm', '43.0895577', '-79.08494359999997', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(8, 7, 'Full Canadian Buffet Lunch at Sheraton Fallsview Restaurant (Optional Add On)', 'Enjoy a full Canadian Buffet Lunch. A fresh, healthy and delicious buffet lunch at the Sheraton Fallsview Restaurant, on the penthouse level of the Sheraton Hotel. You will enjoy a tasty meal while enjoying the spectacular view of the Canadian Horseshoe Falls and American Falls. This is an awesome photo opportunity! ', 'Sheraton on the Falls Hotel, Falls Avenue, Niagara Falls, ON, Canada', '1:30 pm', '43.0910022', '-79.07290309999996', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(9, 7, 'Scenic drive on Niagara Parkway', 'Niagara Parkway has been called \"The Prettiest Sunday Afternoon Drive in the World,\" see for yourself!    The Niagara Parkway is a spectacular drive along the Niagara River.  You can admire the views and the recreational trail is used by pedestrians and is also wheelchair accessible. ', 'Niagara Parkway, Niagara Falls, ON, Canada', '2:30 pm', '43.0650319', '-79.05270569999999', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(10, 7, 'Whirlpool Rapids', 'Experience the natural phenomenon of the Niagara River.  You will witness the power of the Niagara River and watch the white waters of the rapids in the Niagara Gorge.  The waters of the rapids converge, causing them to spin in counterclockwise motion.  ', 'Niagara Falls, ON, Canada', '3:15 pm', '43.0895577', '-79.08494359999997', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(11, 7, 'Floral Clock', 'Between the Botanical Gardens and Queenston Heights Park stands one of the most popular sights to view in Niagara. The Floral Clock is a 12.2-m (40-ft.) diameter working clock that is one of the largest in the world.  Once you have taken all you photos with the colourful clock you can take time to go souvenir shopping or skip the shopping to save time on tour. ', 'Queenston Heights National Historic Site, Niagara Parkway, Queenston, ON, Canada', '3:30 pm', '43.16011799999999', '-79.05296099999998', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(12, 7, 'Queenston Heights Stopover', 'Stopover at Queenston Heights, which borders Canada and the United States with only the Niagara River separating them. Are you a history buff? Come with us and learn about the famous Battle of Queenston Heights. Queenston Heights Park is the site of a War of 1812 battle in which Sir Isaac Brock was killed. A 50-m. (150-ft.) monument, that is perched above the Niagara Escarpment, was built in his honour.  4:00 pm: Stop at the Smallest Chapel in the World! Nobody takes you there, except us, this is a unique destination and a perfect place for more pictures! 4:15 pm: Stopover in Niagara-on-the-lake for 60-75 MINUTES. You will appreciate the quaint shops and boutiques that line Queen Street, the main drag of Niagara-on-the-Lake, as well as the proximity of wineries, brew pubs and even a chocolate factory! ', 'Queenston Heights Park, Niagara Parkway, Niagara-on-the-Lake, ON, Canada', '3:45 pm', '43.159306', '-79.05541099999999', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(13, 7, 'Winery Tour', 'Complimentary wine and grape juice tasting is available.  Be treated as a wine connoisseur at a world-class winery. Buy local-made wines of your choice. World famous Canadian  Ice Wines are available here. ', 'Niagara-on-the-Lake, ON, Canada', '5:30 pm', '43.2549988', '-79.07726159999999', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(14, 7, 'Dropoff - Niagara Falls Small Group Custom Tour - Upto 4 People', 'We drop you back at home safe and sound a lovely day trip to Niagara!', 'Toronto, ON, Canada or Niagara Falls, ON, Canada', '7:00-7:30 pm (or earlier)', '43.653226', '-79.38318429999998', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(15, 5, 'Evening Tour Pickup', 'Free pick up from your hotel lobby in Toronto, Mississauga, Brampton and Etobicoke Hotels, including Hotels near the Toronto Pearson International Airport. 1.5 Hours (90 minutes) drive from Toronto to Niagara Falls. ', 'Toronto, ON, Canada', 'Between 1:00-2:00pm', '43.653226', '-79.38318429999998', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(16, 5, 'Whirlpool Rapids', 'Experience the natural phenomenon of the Niagara River.  You will witness the power of the Niagara River and watch the white waters of the rapids in the Niagara Gorge.  The waters of the rapids converge, causing them to spin in counterclockwise motion.  Board a helicopter ride and experience Niagara Falls from above (optional add-on). ', 'Niagara Falls, ON, Canada', '4:00pm', '43.0895577', '-79.08494359999997', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(17, 5, 'Niagara Falls - Hornblower Boat Cruise', 'Now comes the main attraction!  The majestic Canadian Niagara Falls!  Get up close and personal with Niagara Falls with a FREE Hornblower Boat Cruise (seasonal), you will receive VIP treatment and not have to wait in line.  If the Hornblower cruise is not available then you will enjoy the panoramic view of the Niagara Falls from the Skylon Tower.    ', 'Niagara Falls, ON, Canada', '4:30pm', '43.0895577', '-79.08494359999997', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(18, 5, 'Winery Tour', 'Complimentary wine and grape juice tasting is available.  Be treated as a wine connoisseur at a world-class winery. Buy local made wines of your choice. World famous Canadian  Ice Wines are available here. ', 'Niagara-on-the-Lake, ON, Canada', '6:00pm', '43.2549988', '-79.07726159999999', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(19, 5, 'Discover Niagara-on-the-Lake', 'Spend 45 Minutes strolling around the historical town of Niagara-on-the-lake. Niagara-on-the-Lake was named the Prettiest Town in Canada by Communities in Bloom, you will surely agree! 7:30pm Visit the world\'s smallest chapel. You will hardly see this on the itinerary of other tour operators. This is an amazing place to visit, an excellent photo opportunity.  Do not worry about getting lost!  You will have the free Niagara Falls lanyard with our contact information with you.  This is especially liked by tourists travelling with young children. ', 'Niagara-on-the-Lake, ON, Canada', '6:30pm', '43.2549988', '-79.07726159999999', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(20, 5, 'Visit Queenston Heights', 'Stop at Queenston Heights. Queenston Heights is an extensive hillside area on the Niagara escarpment, centred on a heavily wooded, landscaped park which includes an elegant 57.9 metres (190 foot), classical column containing Sir Isaac Brock\'s grave. The park marks the site of the Battle of Queenston Heights in the War of 1812. Witness the spectacular Floral Clock, over 16,000 bedding plants used to create this attraction. The Floral Clock is a very popular stop on the Niagara Parkway and is photographed almost as often as the Falls!  ', 'Queenston Heights Park, Niagara Parkway, Niagara-on-the-Lake, ON, Canada', '8:00pm', '43.159306', '-79.05541099999999', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(21, 5, 'Full Canadian Buffet Dinner at Sheraton Fallsview Restaurant (Optional Add On)', 'Enjoy a full Canadian Buffet Dinner. A fresh, healthy and delicious buffet dinner at the Sheraton Fallsview Restaurant, on the penthouse level of the Sheraton Hotel. You will enjoy a tasty meal with a lot to choose from while enjoying the spectacular view of the Canadian Horseshoe Falls and American Falls. This is an awesome photo opportunity! ', 'Sheraton Fallsview Hotel u0026 Conference Center, Fallsview Boulevard, Niagara Falls, ON, Canada', '8:30pm', '43.077399', '-79.08293200000003', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(22, 5, 'Fireworks (seasonal)', 'Enjoy the Fireworks every Friday, Sunday and Holidays (contact us to verify).', 'Niagara Falls, ON, Canada', '10:00pm', '43.0895577', '-79.08494359999997', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(23, 5, 'Evening Tour Dropoff ', 'The tour ends back where it started, your camera will be full of memories that will last forever! The end to a perfect evening.', 'Toronto, ON, Canada', '11:30pm -12:00am ', '43.653226', '-79.38318429999998', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(24, 4, 'Day Tour Begins', 'Free pick up from most hotels in Toronto, Mississauga, Brampton and Etobicoke Hotels, including Hotels near the Toronto Pearson International Airport (there is a list of pickup locations in the FAQ section of the website). 1.5 Hours (90 minutes) drive from Toronto to Niagara Falls. ', 'Downtown, Toronto, ON, Canada', '8:30 - 9:30 am', '43.654262', '-79.38597500000003', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(25, 4, 'Arrive at Canadian side of Niagara Falls.', 'You will be able to see the beautiful Niagara Falls even before the bus stops!', 'Niagara Falls, ON, Canada', '11 am', '43.0895577', '-79.08494359999997', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(26, 4, 'Hornblower Niagara Cruise (Seasonal)', 'FREE Admission to Hornblower Niagara Boat Cruise and no waiting in line (All tickets include Fast Track access via the Funicular Incline Railway).  This attraction is seasonal.  If the Hornblower cruise is not available (usually in the winter months) then you will experience either the Journey Behind the Falls attraction, where you travel around in the tunnels behind the Niagara Falls or see the panoramic view of the Niagara Falls from the Skylon Tower (the attraction visited depends on availability).  ', 'Hornblower Niagara Cruises, Niagara Falls, ON, Canada', '11:15 am', '43.088677', '-79.0743622', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(27, 4, 'Explore Niagara Falls', 'Free time to eat lunch, souvenir shop and explore!  If you lose your way, contact the phone number on your lanyard for assistance.', 'Niagara Falls, ON, Canada', '12 pm', '43.0895577', '-79.08494359999997', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(28, 4, 'Full Canadian Buffet Lunch at Sheraton Fallsview Restaurant (Optional Add On)', 'OPTIONAL ADD-ON:  Enjoy a large Canadian Buffet Lunch. This is a healthy alternative to fast food at the Sheraton on the Falls Restaurant.  Enjoy a delicious lunch and a breath taking view of the Falls. ', 'Sheraton on the Falls Hotel, Falls Avenue, Niagara Falls, ON, Canada', '1:30 pm', '43.0910022', '-79.07290309999996', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(29, 4, ' Scenic drive on Niagara Parkway', 'Cruise along the famous Niagara Parkway along the Niagara River and admire the wonderful view.   ', 'Niagara Parkway, Niagara Falls, ON, Canada', ' 2:30 pm', '43.0650319', '-79.05270569999999', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
