(65, 27, 'Winery Tour', 'Complimentary wine and grape juice tasting is available.  Be treated as a wine connoisseur at a world-class winery. Buy local made wines of your choice. World famous Canadian  Ice Wines are available here.', 'Niagara-on-the-Lake, ON, Canada', '6:00pm', '43.2549988', '-79.07726159999999', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(66, 27, 'Discover Niagara-on-the-Lake', 'Spend 45 Minutes strolling around the historical town of Niagara-on-the-lake. Niagara-on-the-Lake was named the Prettiest Town in Canada by Communities in Bloom, you will surely agree! 7:30pm Visit the world’s smallest chapel. You will hardly see this on the itinerary of other tour operators. This is an amazing place to visit, an excellent photo opportunity.  Do not worry about getting lost!  You will have the free Niagara Falls lanyard with our contact information with you.  This is especially liked by tourists travelling with young children. ', 'Niagara-on-the-Lake, ON, Canada', '6:30pm', '43.2549988', '-79.07726159999999', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(67, 27, 'Visit Queenston Heights', 'Stop at Queenston Heights. Queenston Heights is an extensive hillside area on the Niagara escarpment, centred on a heavily wooded, landscaped park which includes an elegant 57.9 metres (190 foot), classical column containing Sir Isaac Brock’s grave. The park marks the site of the Battle of Queenston Heights in the War of 1812. Spectacular Floral Clock. This unique attraction is a very popular stop on the Niagara Parkway and is photographed almost as often as the Falls! ', 'Queenston Heights Park, Niagara Parkway, Niagara-on-the-Lake, ON, Canada', '8:00pm', '43.159306', '-79.05541099999999', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(68, 27, 'Full Canadian Buffet Dinner at Sheraton Fallsview Restaurant (Optional Add On)', 'Enjoy a full Canadian Buffet Dinner. A fresh, healthy and delicious buffet dinner at the Sheraton Fallsview Restaurant, on the penthouse level of the Sheraton Hotel. You will enjoy a tasty meal with a lot to choose from while enjoying the spectacular view of the Canadian Horseshoe Falls and American Falls. This is an awesome photo opportunity! ', 'Sheraton Fallsview Hotel Conference Center, Fallsview Boulevard, Niagara Falls, ON, Canada', '8:30pm', '43.077399', '-79.08293200000003', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(69, 27, 'Fireworks (seasonal)', 'Enjoy the Fireworks every Friday, Sunday and Holidays (contact us to verify).', 'Niagara Falls, ON, Canada', '10:00pm', '43.0895577', '-79.08494359999997', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(70, 27, 'Evening Tour Dropoff ', 'The tour ends back where it started, your camera will be full of memories that will last forever! The end to a perfect evening.', 'Mississauga, ON, Canada', '11:30pm -12:00am ', '43.5890452', '-79.6441198', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
(71, 26, 'Day Tour Begins', 'You will be picked up from your designated Mississauga Hotel or nearby pickup location and travel to Niagara Falls (the trip to Niagara Falls from Mississauga takes around 90 minutes).', 'Mississauga, ON, Canada', '8:30 - 9:30 am', '43.5890452', '-79.6441198', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
