(96, 18, 'Clifton Hill - Niagara Falls Fun', 'The fun never stops at Clifton Hill.  Get a birds eye view in a climate controlled gondola 175 feet above the Falls in the Niagara SkyWheel.  You could also visit the Movieland wax museum and see all your favourite movie, television and music celebrities up close and personal.', 'Clifton Hill, Niagara Falls, ON, Canada', '', '43.0912075', '-79.074411', 1, '2018-09-03 15:03:19'),
