(96, 13, 'fire master', 'master@htmail.com', '', 'We chose to have an air tour of Niagara as part of our Wedding Anniversary. Ian and his staff are very accommodating during the booking process, and he was super friendly. Our pilot Alex made the entire trip worth while, he was very helpful and informative. The tour and views are amazing. [Reviewed on TripAdvisor]', 5, '70.27.89.204', '2018-02-08 13:24:15', 1, '2018-02-08 13:24:15'),
(97, 13, '68 Munchkin', '68munchkin@htmail.com', '', 'What can I say about this - one of the best things I have ever done. Me and my husband had the most amazing trip over the falls. It cost us $30 cab/taxi fair to the airfield from Niagara Falls, about 15 mins drive. The views were fabulous and Alex was one of the nicest people we have ever met. He was so knowledgeable about the area and the history, made our experience even better, he is a credit to this company and we can\\\'t thank him enough for the kindness and help he gave us, especially as my husband doesn\\\'t really like flying or heights. Can\\\'t recommend this trip enough, a must at Niagara. We got some of the best photos ever. [Reviewed on TripAdvisor]', 5, '70.27.89.204', '2018-02-08 13:17:48', 1, '2018-02-08 13:17:48'),
(98, 12, 'Sergio S', 'sergios@htmail.com', '', 'Enjoyed every second of it. \r\nIan picked us up at our hotel exactly on time. Journey to Niagara Airport was extremely comfortable on a brand new chrisler voyager; he is really knowledgeable about the area and there is lots you can learn from him.\r\nThe scenic flight over Niagara falls was amazing and so was the trip on the Maid of the Mist boat at the falls. \r\nHe also took us for wine tasting to a local vineyard where you can learn a lot if you are interested in this kind of things. \r\nReally, I travel the world a lot and do lots of tours like this but rarely I have been so happy. \r\nLooking forward to do the same tours on winter. [Reviewed on TripAdvisor]', 5, '70.27.89.204', '2018-02-08 13:14:42', 1, '2018-02-08 13:14:42'),
(99, 13, 'L Silva', 'lsilva@htmail.com', '', 'Taking a flight over the Niagara falls and the Lake Ontario area was a remarkable experience. Ian was very accommodating regarding the timing of my flight, and was able to give me the most wonderful experience to see all those sights from the air. Definitely worth it. [Reviewed on TripAdvisor]', 5, '70.27.89.204', '2018-02-08 13:11:59', 1, '2018-02-08 13:11:59'),
