(107, 13, 'Aurelia J', 'aureliaj@htmail.com', '', 'It was just perfect!! Ian has been very kind to us and even agreeded to pick us up from our hotel which was very convenient - otherwise we couldn\\\'t have done the tour. Eric (our pilot) and him flew with us and were very knowledgeable about the region. They both answered all our questions. We also flew some extra minutes as we dropped Eric off on the way back -we could enjoy a more than the actual tour so we were very happy. It is completely worth the money. We will definitely recommend this activity to anyone (from any age). Thanks again for having us. [Reviewed on TripAdvisor]', 5, '70.27.89.204', '2018-02-05 14:47:46', 1, '2018-02-05 14:47:46'),
