(114, 13, 'Catrol 1', 'catrol1@htmail.com', '', 'This excursion was amazing! I was a little nervous as it was my first time in a small aircraft and the pilot Alex and his staff took the time to make me feel comfortable and relaxed. They were wonderful and had the right combination of information mixed with laughter to get you to feel ready to go for it! The take off and landing were easy peasy! The sights and photos we saw are incredible. Got to add this to your to do list for Niagara! Best way to mark our 20th wedding anniversary and our son graduating high school [Reviewed on TripAdvisor]', 5, '70.27.89.204', '2018-01-30 14:03:41', 1, '2018-01-30 14:03:41'),
