(125, 13, 'Viv B', 'vivb@htmail.com', '', 'I booked this flight as a surprise for my husbands 50th birthday. \r\nHe was thrilled with the flight &amp; so was I.\r\nAlex our pilot was fabulous, nothing too much trouble &amp; not in any way rushed. A lovely guy &amp; experienced pilot.\r\nThe flight was amazing, it was awesome to see Niagara from the air. We had already been on the Horn Blower night cruise from the Canadian side &amp; Maid of the mist from the American side.\r\nBut how spectacular to see all the falls from the air &amp; the whole region, stretching as far as Toronto.\r\nWe have done a few helicopter flights on previous holidays, Hawaii, Grand Canyon &amp; New York but nothing compares to this airplane tour it was the best - one that will stay in our memories forever.\r\nAwesome, amazing, spectacular the one tour not to be missed.\r\nThank you Alex \r\nV &amp; A \r\nUk [ Reviewed on TripAdvisor]', 5, '67.70.65.190', '2018-01-29 20:02:35', 1, '2018-01-29 20:02:35'),
