(316, 8, 'Jo L', 'jolow@htmail.com', '', 'We are on a tour across Canada and this is one of the options. The staff are excellent and made sure everyone was clipped in and secure. We were lucky to get front seats and what an experience. From the take off to the flight down the river, then he banked over the falls it was amazing. The views of Niagra from the air is one that will remain with me forever. Can\\\'t recommend this trip enough, you have to do it...awesome [As reviewed on TripAdvisor]', 5, '70.54.45.156', '2017-09-21 03:46:55', 1, '2017-09-21 03:46:55'),
