(380, 7, 'Peace Headingly', 'peace@yhoo.com', '', 'Went for  a quick day trip, I was going to go for the normal Day Tour but I wanted to see Skylon Tower and Journey Behind the Falls, so I picked the Private tour which allows you to go anywhere. We went from Toronto to Niagara Falls, it\\\'s a magnificent thing to see.  Try to see everything you can, there are lots of people lots of lineups so purchase the Boat Cruise tickets before and have fun instead of waiting in line.  It is a great experience highly recommended.', 5, '184.148.33.125', '2017-08-03 17:30:30', 1, '2017-08-03 17:30:30'),
(381, 19, 'mariposa rojas', 'mariposa@yhoo.com', '', 'Our family came  from Eastern Europe to check out Niagara and visit the wineries, we toured through the nice countryside.  It was nice, the bus was clean and the wine was great!  Ice wine costs more to taste but I would recommend that you spend and taste the ice wine.', 5, '184.148.33.125', '2017-08-03 14:35:32', 1, '2017-08-03 14:35:32'),
(382, 15, 'Rainn Sinclair', 'raindrops1@htmail.com', '', 'Here for a conference in Toronto, we went out to Niagara Falls when the conference was over.  Loved it!!!!  There\\\'s a lot to see and do!  I definitely recommend the Maid of the Mist or Hornblower or whatever it\\\'s called now it was great!  Journey Behind the Falls was not that thrilling.  The Winery was good as well if you are into wines and wine tasting.  For my group the private tour was the way to go, it\\\'s nice to be with friends and go where we wanted, when we wanted.  Then we were dropped off at the airport and back home.  Niagara Falls is a must see, everyone should go, these guys picked us from Toronto to NIagara Falls.', 5, '184.148.33.125', '2017-08-03 14:29:01', 1, '2017-08-03 14:29:01'),
(383, 5, 'Joy B', 'Joyb@fmail.com', '', 'Our family has been looking forward to travelling to Niagara Falls for a while now.  I finally thought this was a good time, the kids were old enough so we went.  I wanted to go at night because the kids could eat a big dinner and sleep on the bus.  It was a great tour, the kids loved the hornblower cruise and the buildings, they learned a lot.  The guide we had was great.  The kids were so tired at the end they almost missed the fireworks!  Very memorable i\\\'m glad I went with ToNiagara!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-08-02 21:24:32', 1, '2017-08-02 21:24:32'),
(384, 8, 'Carolina S.', 'cseleme@htmail.com', '', 'Awesomeeee [Reviewed on Google Plus]', 5, '70.54.45.156', '2017-08-02 17:55:37', 1, '2017-08-02 17:55:37'),
(385, 8, 'Linda S', 'lslamka@htmail.com', '', 'It was amazing!!! We took our 92 year old Mom for her FIRST Helicopter Ride and it could not have been more PERFECT!!!!!❤ [Reviewed on Google Plus]', 5, '70.54.45.156', '2017-08-02 17:42:35', 1, '2017-08-02 17:42:35');
INSERT INTO `tour_reviews` (`ID`, `tour_id`, `name`, `email`, `website`, `description`, `count_star`, `author_IP`, `created_on`, `status`, `timestamp`) VALUES
(386, 8, 'Ewan L.', 'ewanluke@htmail.com', '', 'Don\\\'t miss out on this if you happen to be in Niagara Falls, absolutely spectacular. Worth everything [As reviewed on TripAdvisor]', 5, '70.54.45.156', '2017-08-02 04:00:34', 1, '2017-08-02 04:00:34'),
(387, 4, 'Addison W', 'addisonw@fmail.com', '', 'We got lucky and booked this trip on a day on which the weather was excellent! not too hot , not too cold. and that added to the comfort that we felt on this trip !! excellent job toniagar guys!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-08-01 16:18:03', 1, '2017-08-01 16:18:03'),
(388, 8, 'James S.', 'jamess@htmail.com', '', 'Having spent the morning seeing the falls from just sbout every angle this is something quite different.\r\n\r\nGives you a different perspective on the size and the overall layout of the falls plus away from the spray you see something more.\r\n\r\nThe staff were very efficient and dealt well with some people who felt they had a right to sit in the front of the helicopter (they didn\\\'t). The pilot banks to both sides so all seats get a great view. [As reviewed on TripAdvisor]', 5, '70.54.45.156', '2017-08-01 01:01:22', 1, '2017-08-01 01:01:22'),
(389, 5, 'Wun Wun', 'azorahai@htmail.com', '', 'Not much to say really, this is an excellent tour!  I went Sunday then made it back home to watch Game of Thrones!  Highly recommend this tour, we should splurged on the buffet though, it seems better than the fast food option we went with.', 5, '64.229.2.125', '2017-07-29 15:54:51', 1, '2017-07-29 15:54:51'),
(390, 7, 'Boss Man202', 'chivery@htmail.com', '', 'I surprised my wife with a lovely excursion to the Falls, it was wonderful, we went a little later in the day, saw the light illuminate the falls and the fireworks and I reserved a nice dinner.  4 stars because the weather was a little rainy.  Would def recommend, especially for valentines day.', 5, '64.229.2.125', '2017-07-29 12:31:21', 1, '2017-07-29 12:31:21'),
(391, 5, 'Franco P', 'francop@dmail.com', '', 'Came here from Vancouver, I thought the night time would be less crowded but it was still very busy, so I can imagine how it\\\'s like in the daytime!  Great tour though', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-07-28 20:30:44', 1, '2017-07-28 20:30:44'),
(392, 8, 'Sean C.', 'scox@htmail.com', '', 'Experience of a lifetime. Although the ride is unfortunately short, it is still a must-do on my list. 10/10 would recommend. [Reviewed on Google Plus]', 5, '70.54.45.156', '2017-07-28 17:39:27', 1, '2017-07-28 17:39:27'),
(393, 4, 'Jason O', 'jasono@fmail.com', '', 'Bought this trip for my parents and they reported back that the trip was good!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-07-28 00:00:38', 1, '2017-07-28 00:00:38'),
(394, 15, 'Cathy S', 'cathys@htmail.com', '', 'My sales team was at a Conference in Toronto, we don\\\'t think we\\\'ll ever be up here again so we decided to make the most of it and take a ToNiagara Private tour.  It was fantastic, we went on the Hornblower and the helicopter and then a winery..  The SUV was comfortable and everyone had a fun adventure.  Definitely would recommend to anyone visiting here or at a conference, Niagara Falls is not to be missed.', 5, '64.229.1.80', '2017-07-27 16:57:49', 1, '2017-07-27 16:57:49'),
(395, 19, 'John Bynard', 'johnb@htmail.com', '', 'Restaurant owner here, we took all of our employees on this Niagara Tour, it was great!  Definitely go on the Hornblower and the buffet meal was good, with all the different dietary restrictions of our employees the buffet was really the only way to go.  It was fun and a great team building activity.  We arrived back in Toronto, relieved of stress and ready to work!', 5, '64.229.1.80', '2017-07-27 16:51:52', 1, '2017-07-27 16:51:52'),
(396, 4, 'Michele Williams', 'michelew@htmail.com', '', 'I was so impressed with the tour - on time, knowledgeable, fun and helpful crew with impeccable driving ability. It was surely worth every dollar spent. We enjoyed every single stop and went berserk at the Niagara-on-the-Lake at all those quaint stores that were there. We shopped for everyone on our list and had great fun doing so. I am so glad I chose your tour. You were the most organized in terms of letting us know the specific routes and exact times plus you never got tired of me calling or emailing you. Also your stop at the Living Water Wayside Chapel was of special importance to me. Alesha and Eli (I hope I have the spellings correct) are the best. Special kudos to them both - they kept us safe and entertained all day.\r\n\r\nGood job To Niagara. Would definitely recommend you to all my friends and family. Wish you all future success.', 5, '64.229.1.80', '2017-07-27 16:46:49', 1, '2017-07-27 16:46:49'),
(397, 8, 'jim h', 'jimh@htmail.com', '', 'My wife and I took the tour over the falls on an overcast day with slight rain. The views were fantastic and the narration was informative. [As reviewed on TripAdvisor]', 5, '70.54.45.156', '2017-07-26 04:03:27', 1, '2017-07-26 04:03:27'),
(398, 8, 'Sena K.', 'senak@htmail.com', '', 'With great pilot and new helicopter i got nice exeperience above Niagara in sky. Thanks to every steps especially smart and hansome pilot. [As reviewed on TripAdvisor]', 5, '70.54.45.156', '2017-07-25 04:04:55', 1, '2017-07-25 04:04:55'),
(399, 4, 'Bianca R', 'bianca@fmail.com', '', 'I had seen the falls when I was kid and went there now after a whole decade! Still amazes me with its beauty! A lot has changed around the falls in ten years!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-07-22 19:18:27', 1, '2017-07-22 19:18:27'),
(400, 5, 'Danka Prostran', 'dprostran66@htmail.com', '', 'I just took this tour last Friday and it was amazing, it was raining in the daytime so I was a little worried but it didn\\\'t rain in the evening.  Falls looked great and the Fireworks were very memorable.  I should have went with the buffet dinner instead of fast food!  All in all I think the evening trip is best.', 5, '64.229.1.80', '2017-07-21 16:01:58', 1, '2017-07-21 16:01:58'),
(401, 15, 'Karl D', 'kdodds@htmail.com', '', 'We were very lucky!  We secured an SUV on very short notice, went to a Winery and hit the Falls and then did some shopping!  Great experience. I would recommend.', 5, '64.229.1.80', '2017-07-21 15:55:15', 1, '2017-07-21 15:55:15'),
(402, 21, 'Chiro Santana', 'chiro1@htmail.com', '', 'I took a group of 52 adults and seniors to Niagara Falls.  There were a lot of dietary restrictions and when you have large groups it is better that everyone eats at the same place so nobody gets lost! The buffet add-on was one of the reasons I booked with ToNiagara also the Hornblower Attraction is a good attraction for large groups not to mention spectacular so I purchased that add on as well for everyone.  ToNIagara picked us up and dropped us off, the bus was comfortable.  Would recommend', 5, '64.229.1.80', '2017-07-21 15:48:25', 1, '2017-07-21 15:48:25'),
(403, 8, 'Liz F.', 'lizf@htmail.com', '', 'As the other reviewer stated, a front seat is so much better and fortunately, my granddaughter and I had the front. It\\\'s only a 10 minute ride and a bit pricey. Since this was her vacation trip, we splurged on her. My husband sati this one out because of the price. [As reviewed on TripAdvisor]', 5, '70.54.45.156', '2017-07-21 04:06:50', 1, '2017-07-21 04:06:50'),
(404, 5, 'Jane F', 'janef@fmail.com', '', 'Great trip. Would do it again and would recommend. Thanks !!!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-07-20 20:39:33', 1, '2017-07-02 20:39:33'),
(405, 8, 'deborah d', 'deborahdawn@htmail.com', '', 'By far one of THE best experiences I\\\'ve ever had. I can\\\'t recommend enough. I can\\\'t even say much about it because you can\\\'t accurately describe it but flying over the falls gives you such a different pespective of this awesome force of nature. Great photo opportunity although it is throgh a window! There is an on board pre recorded guide telling you a bit about the area and falls. You get your picture taken by and sitting in the helicopter with option to buy before you leave but they\\\'re actually quite reasonable for a momento. There is also a gift shop. I\\\'d recommend going earlier in the morning to avoid queues. The helicopters all look new and well maintained and I didn\\\'t feel unsafe at any point - the staff ensure you are properly strapped in etc before taking off. Really an excellent experience - don\\\'t miss out! [As reviewed on TripAdvisor]', 5, '70.54.45.156', '2017-07-19 04:08:22', 1, '2017-07-19 04:08:22'),
(406, 4, 'Gordon S', 'gordona@fmail.com', '', 'Excellent experience! Both our tour gudie Harry and the pilot from the chopper , did a great job!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-07-17 22:05:04', 1, '2017-07-17 22:05:04'),
(407, 4, 'Laura M', 'Lauram@fmail.com', '', 'Planned a trip wth my husband and a friend and her husband. Great company and awesome trip!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-07-15 22:20:13', 1, '2017-07-15 22:20:13'),
(408, 4, 'Alex V', 'alexv@dmail.com', '', 'The Falls are a breath taking sight!! Especially loved the view from the chopper. That is a MUST do!! Also the lunch buffet is an impressive spread. Food lover like me , really enjoyed :)', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-07-15 20:01:12', 1, '2017-07-15 20:01:12'),
(409, 4, 'Miguel K', 'migueld@wmail.com', '', 'Highlight of our trip was the helicopter flight. It was truly beautiful !! Our pilot was friendly and made the flight fun. Would definitely do this again and recommend to anyone!!!!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-07-14 21:39:49', 1, '2017-07-14 21:39:49'),
(410, 5, 'Scott A', 'scotta@fmail.com', '', 'Excellent trip, great memories, great tour guide. Niagara at night was awesome!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-07-13 20:56:43', 1, '2017-07-13 20:56:43'),
(411, 4, 'Richard O\\\'Carroll', 'rocarroll@g-mail.com', '', 'Went on the tour with an Airtours coach with my 2 grownup kids as well as my 14 year old. From the start we were welcomed by both host Galicia and driver Eli. This welcome and care genuinely extended throughout the trip.  The hornblower experience on the river was the first activity was incredible. Get to the front asap. Wear a short pants and light tee shirt and sandles as despite a light plastic poncho you will get wet. Well worth it and you do dry off. I had a small backpack with a change which kept dry.  The additional cost of a buffet lunch at the Sheradon hotel was worth it. Too much food !! All delicious. Go to the balcony at the back of the dining area for wonderful photographs of the 2 waterfalls over both shoulders, particularly when everyone else is queuing for food, because it is a small balcony and there will be queues after dinner. THEN get diner when the queues there will have dissipated.  Visit Fort George at Niagra by the Lake which is an option if you like history. The layout, buildings, life portrayed and if you arrive on time a reinactment of soldiers musket firing can be seen during the Summer.  Stops at a souvineers shop, market centre and a winery was also a great was to buy unique souvineers. A very enjoyable day that kept grown up kids engaged as well.', 5, '184.148.33.53', '2017-07-13 01:28:25', 1, '2017-07-13 01:28:25'),
(412, 8, 'Rosie S.', 'rosie@htmail.com', '', 'Showed up with an \\\"older\\\" coupon and thought I was going to be told it was full price, instead she said \\\"Oh no! I mean you get more off than this says\\\" and applied the additional discount without me asking! They held our valuables behind the desk, got on the radio to tell them we had a big group coming so we could ride together and they ran a very efficient operation. This was a big bucket list item for the family and majority of the group\\\'s first helicopter ride and they couldn\\\'t stop talking about it! I couldn\\\'t hear any of the commentary in the back but honestly didn\\\'t much care! ;) Got great pictures, great memories - keep doing what you do! Only feedback would be to tell people you are going to be taking multiple pictures, you will sell more! Ours all had someone trying to get a camera ready or looking down or eyes closed or whatnot. Didn\\\'t damper our experience, just would bring you more revenue if someone gave a little more guidance. :) [As reviewed on TripAdvisor]', 5, '70.54.45.156', '2017-07-12 16:18:19', 1, '2017-07-12 16:18:19'),
(413, 5, 'Herman B', 'hermanb@fmail.com', '', 'Tour guide was awesome! Took the time to take pictures of our group throughout the trip. Pointed out areas of interest. The falls at night are a must see and the online pics defnitely don\\\'t do it justice!!!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-07-10 20:37:08', 1, '2017-07-10 20:37:08'),
(414, 5, 'Vincent G', 'vincentg@fmail.com', '', 'One of my favourite tour experiences!!!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-07-09 20:23:55', 1, '2017-07-09 20:23:55'),
(415, 8, 'Geoff M', 'gmanser@htmail.com', '', 'This is it! The best way to see Niagara Falls. \r\nWhile this is expensive it\\\'s actually great value. We had three in our group which meant it was pricey but the view is stunning. \r\nThe pilot didn\\\'t speak . . . at all . . . which is fine because he was focused on his job which is great. \r\nThere is a recorded audio track which plays as you fly and the helicopter is surprisingly quiet. \r\nI\\\'d do this again. Great fun and the views are simply stunning. [As reviewed on TripAdvisor]', 5, '70.54.45.156', '2017-07-07 04:02:41', 1, '2017-07-04 04:02:41'),
(416, 5, 'Jenny Chan', 'jennychan@toniagaracustomer.com', '', 'Excellent service! Experienced tour guide well managed the itinerary even though heavy traffic on the way to the falls. Good communication before and throughout the tour. The boat experience was terrific! Good view for dinner at Sheraton hotel. So we could see the light projection on the falls as well as fireworks on the US side whilst we had dinner. Memorable experience to see the fireworks on the falls. Highly recommend!', 5, '174.91.78.186', '2017-07-06 17:40:10', 1, '2017-07-06 17:40:10'),
(417, 4, 'Shabana E', 'shabana@dmail.com', '', 'Have been to the falls before but this is the first time we did the chopper ride! glad I took that add on! Worth every penny !!!:)', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-07-05 21:45:00', 1, '2017-07-05 21:45:00'),
(418, 8, 'Jan J.', 'janj@htmail.com', '', 'went there in the early afternoon. no waiting time, took maybe 10 minutes until were were seated in the helicopter and ready to fly.\r\nthe price of round about 100EUR per person is quite expensive for a 10 minute flight, but in my opinion definitely worth it. you\\\'ll get an amazing view from the top of the falls! you also get a audio guide in 5 or more languages.[As reviewed on TripAdvisor]', 5, '70.54.45.156', '2017-07-05 04:12:00', 1, '2017-07-05 04:12:00'),
(419, 4, 'Danny P', 'dannyp@fmail.com', '', 'Everything was perfect! Bus arrived on time, and took us to the view points, the lunch is great value for money and of course all views were awesome ! Had a fun time!!!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-07-04 20:29:35', 1, '2017-07-04 20:29:35'),
(420, 4, 'Joanna F', 'joanna@fmail.com', '', 'Absolutely breathtaking!My first visit there and I know I will not forget it :) Thanks toniagara!!!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-07-01 19:51:34', 1, '2017-07-01 19:51:34'),
(421, 8, 'Erick M.', 'emichael@htmail.com', '', 'The view from the ride is incredible and the staff was very nice and accommodating! [Reviewed on Google Plus]', 5, '70.54.45.156', '2017-06-30 01:45:33', 1, '2017-06-30 01:45:33'),
(422, 4, 'Andrew P', 'andrewp@fmail.com', '', 'Celebrated my 65th birthday on this trip. The wonderful company my wife and a family with young children made this a memorable experience I will cherish!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-06-29 22:09:49', 1, '2017-06-29 22:09:49'),
(423, 5, 'Dat N', 'datn@dmail.com', '', 'I came for the fireworks and I saw what I came for and I recommend it to any and everyone.', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-06-28 20:27:43', 1, '2017-06-28 20:27:43'),
(424, 4, 'Joe D', 'joed@fmail.com', '', 'Easy and convenient reservation. On time pick up. Buffet food is not that great so maybe skip that add on and get your own food :)', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-06-26 14:32:28', 1, '2017-06-26 14:32:28'),
(425, 4, 'Randy &amp; Sheila Hildebrandt', 'test@sdfajlk.com', '', 'Hi Nick!\r\n\r\nWe had our tour yesterday of Niagara Falls. It was a wonderful day and the weather was perfect!\r\n\r\nAlicia was our tour guide and she was excellent and very nice to everyone. She made sure she knew everyone\\\'s name and where they were from. \r\n\r\nEli was our driver and was also very kind. \r\n\r\nI would highly recommend this tour and may bring  some more of my family here in September for a trip and another tour of the falls. \r\n\r\n\r\nThank you!', 5, '174.91.78.186', '2017-06-26 01:01:36', 1, '2017-06-26 01:01:36'),
(426, 4, 'Chip M', 'chipm@fmail.com', '', 'The tour itself was great ! would recommend though to book it on a non-weekend day so that its not that crowded in the bus!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-06-25 14:11:15', 1, '2017-06-25 14:11:15'),
(427, 5, 'Andara Jenkley', 'beautiful@gmail.com1', '', 'I would recommend to anyone and everyone, just bring snacks and they give you a mug when you leave to remember the trip!', 5, '64.229.3.74', '2017-06-20 01:33:53', 1, '2017-06-20 01:33:53'),
(428, 4, 'Chris M', 'chrism@dmail.com', '', 'Please make sure that you wear comfy shoes and eat light on the trip cause there ample walking around and standing:)!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-06-16 23:43:25', 1, '2017-06-16 23:43:25'),
(429, 4, 'Chris H', 'chrish@fmail.com', '', 'This tour was the best tour we have ever taken. It was totally worth the money. Pickup and drop off times from our hotel were exactly what we were told they would be. I highly recommend this tour to anyone!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-06-13 19:41:25', 1, '2017-06-13 19:41:25'),
(430, 5, 'James T', 'jamest@fmail.com', '', 'A friend of mine and his gf is already gonna be taking this tour next week on my recommendation! that should say it all :) Good coverage of all interesting spots !!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-06-12 20:53:57', 1, '2017-06-12 20:53:57'),
(431, 4, 'Wes D', 'wesd@fmail.com', '', 'Great day great. Tour guide  was amazing. would recommend to anyone :)', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-06-12 19:38:38', 1, '2017-06-12 19:38:38'),
(432, 4, 'Rosie D', 'rosied@fmail.com', '', 'Great trip. The scenery of course was beautiful at Niagara. I appreciated the science and history information given by the guide. I would definitely do it again. Thanks !', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-06-12 19:34:29', 1, '2017-06-12 19:34:29'),
(433, 4, 'Clarita J', 'claritaj@fmail.com', '', 'Had an amazing trip!!! With Harry our able guide who was so informed and really entertained us all along, managing to do all the stops in a timely manner. It was an awesome trip...and we made it all in good time. Thanks ToNiagara!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-06-12 18:50:32', 1, '2017-06-12 18:50:32'),
(434, 4, 'Lisa W', 'lisaw@fmail.com', '', 'Great day! We booked the helicopter flight option and lunch buffet option, our guide was fabulous, very knowledgeable. A must do...!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-06-12 18:47:11', 1, '2017-06-12 18:47:11'),
(435, 8, 'Jen C.', 'jciszek@htmail.com', '', 'We come sit and watch the helicopter every week with my 3 year old son as he just loves watching them take off. Yesterday he finally decided he wanted to take his 1st ride with his grandma ( this is HUGE as he is scared of everything), I cannot tell you how amazing ALL the staff was to them to make this a special experience for him. Thank you Thank you Thank you for making this an amazing memory for him!!!!! [Reviewed on Google Plus]', 5, '70.54.45.156', '2017-06-11 17:37:42', 1, '2017-06-11 17:37:42'),
(436, 4, 'toniagara', 'admin@woolance.com', '', 'Amazing tour! No complains really. I would recommend it ! Thanks ToNiagara!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-06-10 20:19:38', 1, '2017-06-10 20:19:38'),
(437, 4, 'Kaari A', 'Kaari@fmail.com', '', 'This is truly a gorgeous place! But words won\\\'t do it any justice! You just have to be there!! ToNiagara is a good value for the money you pay for this trip. Wish we had taken the chopper ride!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-06-09 20:15:10', 1, '2017-06-09 20:15:10'),
(438, 5, 'Wesley A', 'wesleya@fmail.com', '', 'As you alk by the Falls , the first thing you see is Horseshoe falls that totally mesmerizes you ! The view of actual Niagara from the Canadian side is much better than the one on US I believe! The hornblower is fun! Everyone on the boat was having so much fun!!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-06-09 20:08:52', 1, '2017-06-09 20:08:52'),
(439, 5, 'Fatima D', 'fatimad@fmail.com', '', 'The tour is kid-friendly, which was a plus for me! Fun times for adults too! Liked our tour guide a lot ! And the falls at night is a thing of beauty!:)', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-06-09 20:04:07', 1, '2017-06-09 20:04:07'),
(440, 5, 'Gonazalo L', 'gonzalo@dmail.com', '', 'This was the best tour i\\\'ve ever been on.', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-06-08 21:32:51', 1, '2017-06-08 21:32:51'),
(441, 4, 'Dennis M', 'dennism@fmail.com', '', 'Trip was good! You have to walk a lot so be prepared for that. But then you can have a nice nap on the ride back on the bus!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-06-08 19:43:14', 1, '2017-06-08 19:43:14'),
