(604, 4, 'William G', 'williambas@gmaildo.com', '', 'The tour was good.  I would have liked to stop at different venues and for longer.  The boat ride is exhilarating but too short.  A little more time would make this trip a 5 out of 5.', 5, '174.91.77.145', '2017-02-14 01:23:08', 1, '2017-02-14 01:23:08'),
(605, 5, 'Julio K', 'juliok@fmail.com', '', 'I came to know that July onwards it gets very crowded on the tours so we chose to go end of May-ish. So our group wasnt so large and that in my opinion made for a much more pleasant trip. More relaxed too. Evening falls are quite the sight!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-02-13 19:56:57', 1, '2017-02-13 19:56:57'),
(606, 5, 'Javier D', 'javierm@dmail.com', '', 'I took this tour strictly for the fireworks and I was not disappointed.  I was wondering why evening tours are Fridays and Sundays only....now I know!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-02-13 17:25:11', 1, '2017-02-13 17:25:11'),
