(608, 5, 'Ken K', 'kenk@fmail.com', '', 'I’ve been on tours all around the world.  I must say this tour is much better organised than 99% of the other tours I’ve been on plus the fireworks made all the difference!  My complaint is just that I would have like to have more free time (walkabout/explore) so I could do some more adventuring as I like to call.  The bus was clean, quiet, comfortable and safe so more free time would have been great.  I love Canada!!!!\r\n Pros – Comfortable seats, air conditioning, picked up on time, free bottled water\r\nCons – not enough time wine tasting, was looking forward to more wine', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-02-07 21:51:37', 1, '2017-02-07 21:51:37'),
(609, 5, 'Alaan G', 'alaand@fmail.com', '', 'The paved walking path alongside the falls is such a great path for a leisurely stroll. Beautiful view and lots of picture taking opportunities! The tour guide for our group was especially great. We all had a great time ! Thank you!', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-02-07 19:36:38', 1, '2017-02-07 19:36:38'),
