(619, 4, 'Benjamin F', 'benjamin@hotmail1234.com', '', 'I always dread going on a tour and having bad weather but we had great weather!  The kids loved it.  Well most of it, the souvenir shopping bored them but they loved the falls and going on the boat which was wet but fun we got to take lots of pictures.', 5, '174.91.77.145', '2017-01-24 02:53:33', 1, '2017-01-24 02:53:33'),
(620, 4, 'Tyler G', 'tylersmith@hotmail1234.com', '', 'I travel to Niagara Falls quite a lot, I took a trip in the winter this time and it was like visiting a different place!  Seeing the ice formations gave the tour a different feel.  Cold but highly recommended...!!', 5, '174.91.77.145', '2017-01-24 00:54:24', 1, '2017-01-24 00:54:24'),
