(622, 5, 'Wendy F', 'wendyf@dmail.com', '', 'We spent the whole day at the Falls and didn’t get a chance to take any pictures as my phone battery died.  To anyone reading this post:  Charge your phone battery the night before and bring an extra charged so you can take all the photos you want.', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-01-18 22:14:59', 1, '2017-01-18 22:14:59'),
