(628, 5, 'Ruth I', 'ruthie@dmail.com', '', 'I booked this tour with my husband and two kids, the bus came on time and the tour was great, it was a little too long for our young children and they were itching to go back to the hotel by the end.  They slept most of the way home though, it is a long tour and a full day.  If you take the children I would suggest you bring some toys or something to keep them entertained on the bus ride to Niagara Falls.', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-01-02 22:09:49', 1, '2017-01-02 22:09:49'),
(629, 4, 'Kerry H', 'kerryh@dmail.com', '', 'My friend and I were celebrating retirement and decide to visit Canada for the first time (we\\\'re from sunny Iowa).  Beautiful country, very clean, Niagara Falls was perfect! loved the Floral Clock and I striked  Helicopter tour off my bucket list!  The aerial view of the Falls was magnificent.  A great day, glad I had the chance to experience it.', 5, '174.91.76.222', '2017-01-01 17:03:05', 1, '2017-01-01 17:03:05'),
