(11, 'Niagara Falls,Niagara Falls Boat Tours', '', 'Canada', 'Falls Fireworks Cruise', 'falls-fireworks-cruise', '(May 18 â€“ October 8)', 'Niagara Falls Fireworks Cruise | Book Tickets Online â€“ Niagara Falls Tour', 'Niagara Falls Fireworks Cruise', 'Niagara Falls Fireworks Cruise - Enjoy a magical evening with the Hornblower Boat Cruise. View Falls illumination and fireworks. Seasonal attraction. Check dates!', '<h3 class=\"heading3\">HORNBLOWER BOAT CRUISE â€“ SUMMER FIREWORKS!</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"m_txt\">\r\n          <p><strong>Niagara Falls Fireworks Cruise â€“ $39.95 per Adult ticket (Seats are Limited, BOOK TODAY!)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n          <p>In the summer months fireworks light up the Niagara evening sky!  What better way to witness the dazzling displays than on a Hornblower Niagara Falls Fireworks Cruise.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"read-more\">\r\n<p>This popular evening cruise departs each evening at 9:30PM in the summer months for a 40 minute cruise adventure on a state-of the-art 700-passenger Catamaran boat.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Niagara Falls', '40 minutes', '3', '', '', 'CA', 'Adults Price', 39.95, '', '', ' ', 0, '', 'Children (5-12 years) ', 35.95, '', 'Infants (0-4 years) ', 0, 'Free', '', '', '', 'Mist Poncho', '', '', '<p><strong>Falls Illumination Cruise (Evening): All sales are final. Not for exchange, resale or transfer.</strong><br>\r\nAll passengers, including children under the age of 5, are required to have a ticket to gain entry to the boat.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Hornblower reserves the right at any time to cancel tours, change departure &amp; arrival times. Only cancelled tours are subject to refund, less any service charge, with no further amount than the face value of the ticket available for compensation.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"read-more2\">\r\n<p>Please arrive in the designated boarding area at least 20 minutes before departure. All passengers and carry-on items are subject to search. Restricted and dangerous articles may not be brought on board. If you buy a ticket, you consent to have your image or likeness appear in any live or recorded video or other transmission or reproduction. Submitting an order in person, via telephone, online or via fax indicates your agreement to these terms and conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Niagara Falls Tour and Hornblower is not associated with the fireworks show and cannot guarantee the show will occur, nor the timing/length of the show.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Niagara Falls Tour is a ticketing agent for Hornblower Niagara Cruises.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>', '', '', '20180820034034_596.jpg', '20180820034034_768.jpg', '', 'asd', 5, 1, 23, 8, '2018-08-20 15:40:34'),
(12, 'Niagara Falls,Airplane Tours', 'Niagara Air Tours', 'Canada', 'Toronto to Niagara Falls Day Tour With Lunch & 30 Minute Airplane Tour', 'toronto-to-niagara-falls-day-tour-with-lunch-and-30-minute-airplane-tour', ' ', 'Toronto to Niagara Falls Day Tour With Lunch, 30-Minute Airplane Tour | Niagara Falls Tour', ' ', 'The most exciting tour of Niagara Falls, 10 hours duration. Includes lunch, a 30-minute airplane tour, FREE Hornblower boat ride, winery tour & more. Book your tour online!', '<h3 class=\"heading3\">Bus Tour, Airplane Tour, Boat Cruise and Lunch All Rolled Into One Fun Day!</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"m_txt\">\r\n<p>This all-in-one Niagara Falls Day Tour will allow you to see Niagara Falls from Land, Water and Air!</p>\r\n<p>First, see Niagara Falls from the sky with a 30 minute airplane ride over the beautiful Niagara Region landscape.</p>\r\n<div class=\"read-more\">\r\n<p>Then it is time to board the Hornblower Boat Cruise, Niagara\'s most popular attraction and take a 20 minute cruise up to the Great Horseshoe Falls.&nbsp; During the Winter months, the cruise is not available and you will be take to Niagara\'s Fury attraction, a 4D interactive theatre.</p>\r\n<p>Lunch is served at the Niagara Golf Club and then off for a Winery tour and wine tasting at the exquisite Konzelmann Estate Winery.</p>\r\n<p>Booking this luxury day tour is simple by selecting the Green \"Book This Tour\" button.</p>\r\n</div></div>', 'Niagara Falls', '10 Hours', '31', '', '', 'CA', 'Adults', 399, '', '', 'Seniors', 399, '', 'Children', 399, '', ' ', 0, '', '', '', '', '<ul class=\"inclu_list\"><li>Hornblower</li>\r\n<li>Wine Tour</li>\r\n<li>Wine Tasting</li>\r\n<li>Airplane Tour</li>\r\n<li>Lunch</li>\r\n</ul>', '', 'Please arrive at 6:45AM in the Crew Check-in Lobby, at the Chelsea Hotel, 33 Gerrard St W, Toronto, ON M5G 1Z4', 'Once the trip is booked and confirmed <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">NO REFUNDS</span> will be provided unless your tour is cancelled due to poor weather conditions.&nbsp;', '<div class=\"txt\">\r\n                  <strong>Where do we meet and at what time?</strong>\r\n<p>Please arrive at 6:45AM in the Crew Check-in Lobby, at the Chelsea Hotel, 33 Gerrard St W, Toronto, ON M5G 1Z4</p>\r\n\r\n<strong>Will we be crossing into the United States on the plane trip?</strong>\r\n<p>No, you will not be crossing into the United States.</p>\r\n<div class=\"read-more2\">\r\n<strong>Will I get wet on the Hornblower Boat Ride?</strong>\r\n<p>The Hornblower will provide ponchos but you may still get wet, you are welcome to bring a change of clothing which you can leave on the bus.</p>\r\n\r\n<strong>Is there an age restriction for this tour?</strong>\r\n<p>The legal drinking age in Canada is 19 years old, individuals under the age of 19 can still visit the winery but must be attended by a parent or guardian</p>\r\n\r\n<strong>What is your cancellation policy?</strong>\r\n<p>Other than weather or operator cancellations, if the trip is cancelled for any other reason NO REFUND will be issued.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'During the winter months (from November to April) the Hornblower Boat is unavailable, instead you will be taken to the Niagaraâ€™s Fury attraction. Niagaraâ€™s Fury is a 4D, interactive, 360 degree theater which outlines the history of Niagara Falls.', '20180820040540_535.jpg', '20180820040540_107.jpg', '', 'asd', 5, 1, 32, 9, '2018-08-20 16:05:40'),
(13, 'Niagara Falls,Airplane Tours', 'Niagara Air Tours', 'Canada', 'Niagara Falls Grand Airplane Tour ', 'niagara-falls-airplane-tour', '(30 mins)', 'Niagara Falls Grand Airplane Tour | Niagara Falls Tour', ' ', 'Thrilling 30-minute ride along the Niagara River. View majestic Niagara Falls, picturesque Niagara region. Fly over Adam Beck Power Plant, Rainbow Bridge, Niagara Whirlpool and other landmarks. Bring your cameras for some unique photos.', '<h3 class=\"heading3\"><p>Witness the Beauty of Niagara From Above</p>\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"m_txt\">\r\n          <p>This exclusive 30 minute airplane tour has been specifically designed to capture the Niagara Region\'s most astonishing attractions such as the natural wonder of Niagara Falls, Niagara-on-the-Lake, Lake Ontario, the Hydro Power Dams and much more!</p>\r\n<div class=\"read-more\">\r\n<p>Booking your airplane adventure is fast and easy, simply click one of the Green \"Book This Tour\" button and reserve a flight date and time.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n          </div>', 'Niagara Falls', '30 Minutes', '65', '', '', 'CA', '1 Person', 199, '', '', '2 Person', 259, '', '3 Person', 389, '', ' ', 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<div class=\"txt\">\r\n                  <strong>When I arrive at St. Catharines/Niagara District Airport, where do I go?</strong>\r\n                  <p>Come to Hangar 22 and staff will assist you.</p>\r\n\r\n                  <strong>Do I need to bring anything?</strong>\r\n                  <p>Please dress appropriately for the weather and remember to bring a camera.</p>\r\n\r\n                  <strong>Are there any weight/height restrictions for the plane?</strong>\r\n                  <p>If you can fit on standard airplane seat, you can will be able to fit onto the airplane. There are no height restrictions.</p>\r\n<div class=\"read-more2\">\r\n                  <strong>Can infants/children take this tour?</strong>\r\n                  <p>Yes, infants and children and ride on the airplane.</p>\r\n\r\n                  <strong>Do I need a passport?</strong>\r\n                  <p>A passport is not necessary.</p>\r\n\r\n                  <strong>How many people does the plane seat?</strong>\r\n                  <p>The airplane sits 3 people (everybody gets a window seat)</p>\r\n\r\n                  \r\n                  <strong>How safe are small aircraft?</strong>\r\n                <p>All airplanes are licensed by Transport Canada and subject to rigorous safety inspections</p>\r\n\r\n                \r\n                <strong>Do you fly in the winter?</strong>\r\n                <p>Yes, Fall and Winter in the Niagara Region is beautiful.</p>\r\n\r\n                \r\n                <strong>What happens if there is bad weather and you cannot fly?</strong>\r\n                <p>If your flight is cancelled due to bad weather we will reschedule when possible, if not we will provide a full reimbursement.</p>\r\n\r\n                \r\n                <strong>What is your cancellation policy?</strong>\r\n                <p>Other than weather or operator cancellations, if the trip is cancelled for any other reason NO REFUND will be issued.</p>\r\n</div>  \r\n                  </div>', '', '20180820045657_404.jpg', '20180820045657_241.jpg', '', 'asd', 5, 1, 23, 10, '2018-08-20 16:56:57'),
(14, 'Home,Niagara Falls,Private Tours', 'Family Tours,History & Culture,Sightseeing tours', 'Canada', 'Toronto to Niagara Falls Half Day Private Tour', 'toronto-to-niagara-falls-half-day-private-tour-upto-7-people', '(upto 7 people)', 'Toronto to Niagara Falls Half Day Tour - Up To 7 People | Niagara Falls Tour', 'Best Niagara Falls Sightseeing Tours, Tour Packages, Day Tour, Evening Tour, Small Group Custom Tour, Private Tour, Group Tours', 'Your Tour, Your Way. This Toronto to Niagara Falls Half Day Tour is ideal for those who cannot stay in Niagara for a full day', '<h3 class=\"heading3\"><p>Toronto to Niagara Falls Half-Day Private Tour (Upto 7 Passengers) - 6 Hours</p>\r\n\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"m_txt\">\r\n<p>The Half Day Private Tour is perfect for those who cannot spend their entire day in Niagara Falls: </p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"read-more\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>People who need to catch an early flight</li>\r\n<li>Families with small children, who may not want to visit wineries or stay on a longer tour</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Individuals who just want to see the Falls and visit a few attractions (perhaps to take a Helicopter Tour or Hornblower Boat Cruise)</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Business colleagues</li>\r\n\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n          <p>Booking a tour can be done safely online.&nbsp; Simply select the Green \"Book This Tour\" button and choose the Addons you would like (i.e. Hornblower Boat Cruise tickets, Lunch Buffet, Helicopter Tour, etc)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Niagara Falls Tour will then confirm your tour and email you a tentative itinerary with pickup/dropoff details as well as any attractions you would like to visit.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>A driver/tour guide and 7 passenger tour vehicle will be provided to you for upto 6 hours. </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Please Note:</strong> Customer pays for meals (unless purchased as an Add-On) and all entrance fees to any attractions visited. The tour schedule below is an example of where you could go. With a custom tour the attractions 