(33, 'Niagara Falls', 'Sightseeing tours', 'USA', 'Canadian Rainbow Illumination Evening Tour Niagara Falls, Ontario', 'canadian-rainbow-illumination-evening-tour-niagara-falls-ontario', 'Half Day Trip (4 Hours)', 'Evening Tour Of Niagara Falls Canada From Niagara Falls USA | Niagara Falls Tour', 'Evening Tour Of Niagara Falls Canada From Niagara Falls USA | Niagara Falls Tour', 'Four-hour tour of Niagara Falls Canada, includes Hornblower Boat Cruise, Floral Clock and more! Free pickup/dropoff from Niagara Falls USA hotels.', '<div class=\"m_txt\">\r\n<h3 class=\"heading3\">Canadian Rainbow Illumination Evening Bus Tour</h3>\r\n<p>Come and see the Niagara Falls lit up in the Evening on a Daily Illumination Evening Bus Tour. </p>\r\n<div class=\"read-more\">\r\n<p>Bring your passport and spend a day on the Canadian Side of Niagara Falls!</p>\r\n<p>This 4 hour tour will take you to all the popular attractions on the Canadian side of the Falls including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Hornblower Boat Cruise</li>\r\n<li>Niagara Whirlpool</li>\r\n<li>Floral Clock</li>\r\n<li>Souvenir shopping at Table Rock</li>\r\n<li>Much more!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Niagara Falls', '4 Hours', '0', '', '', 'US', 'Price', 104.95, ' ', '', ' ', 0, ' ', 'Children (5-12 years)', 74.95, ' ', 'Infants (0-4 years)', 0, ' Free', '', '', '', '<ul class=\"inclu_list\">\r\n<li>Hornblower Boat Cruise</li>\r\n<li>Escalation up the Skylon Tower for a bird\'s eye view of the Niagara Falls</li>\r\n<li>FREE return pass to go back and visit the Skylon Tower on your own</li>\r\n<li>Guided Tour of Niagara Falls, Ontario and surrounding region with full licensed guide/driver</li>\r\n</ul>', '', '<p>Complimentary Pickup from most downtown Niagara Falls USA hotels (you must contact the number provided on your ticket at least 24 hours before your tour and provide your pickup destination).</p>\r\n<p>You must present a printed copy of your electronic voucher to your guide at time of boarding</p>\r\n<p>Border c