(38, 'Niagara Falls', 'Sightseeing tours', 'Canada', 'Niagara Falls Whirlpool Boat Tour â€“ Jetdome Boat Ride', 'niagara-falls-whirlpool-jetdome-boat-tour', '(An Exciting Ride Down the Niagara River Rapids)', 'Niagara Whirlpool Domed Jet Boat Tour | Niagara Falls Tour', ' ', 'Stay dry in a domed jet boat while cruising down the Niagara Rapids. Departures from Niagara Falls & Niagara-on-the-Lake. Book now! View Niagara Whirlpool, Niagara Gorge!', '<h3 class=\"heading3\">Have a Wet and Wild Adventure on a Whirlpool Jet Boat</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"m_txt\">\r\n          <p><strong>Jetdome Option (stay dry on this boat)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Experience the thrill of riding along the Niagara River rapids without getting wet!</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"read-more\">\r\n\r\n<p>No need to bring a change of clothing with the Jetdome Whirlpool boat.  This trip allows customers to travel through the Devil\'s Hole Rapids in a covered Whirlpool Jet Boat.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>The 45 minute boat tour will take you deep into the Niagara Gorge, passing through the famous Niagara Whirlpool and into the Devil\'s Hole Rapids.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<table class=\"tbl_wet_jet\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n\r\n\r\n<tbody>\r\n\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n<th>Niagara Falls Departure Times</th>\r\n\r\n\r\n<th>April 28 â€“ May 18</th>\r\n\r\n\r\n<th>May 19 â€“ June 22</th>\r\n\r\n\r\n<th>June 23 â€“ Sept. 3</th>\r\n\r\n\r\n<th>Sept. 4 â€“ Oct. 21</th>\r\n\r\n\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n<td><strong>Jetdome Boat</strong><br>\r\nNo change of clothing needed</td>\r\n\r\n\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">2:00 PM</td>\r\n\r\n\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">2:00 PM</td>\r\n\r\n\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">11:00 AM</td>\r\n\r\n\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">2:00 PM</td>\r\n\r\n\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n</tbody>\r\n\r\n\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"book_tour_big\"><a href=\"#\">I\'m Ready to Book This T