(15, 'Niagara Falls,Private Tours', 'Family Tours,History & Culture,Sightseeing tours', 'Canada', 'Niagara Falls Small Group Custom Tour', 'niagara-falls-small-group-custom-tour', ' (1-7-people)', 'Niagara Falls Small Group Custom Tour 1-7 People | Niagara Falls Tour', ' ', 'Greater Toronto Area pickup/dropoffs. Full day Niagara Falls Canada tour. Perfect for families/friends. Create an itinerary. Online booking is easy. Check price, other details.', '<h3 class=\"heading3\"><p>Take The Tour Your Way</p>\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"m_txt\">\r\n          <p>Our Full Day Private Tours are made for people who would like to see Niagara Falls their own way, where they can visit the attractions they want to see and leave when they choose.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Private Tours are perfect for:</p>\r\n<div class=\"read-more\">\r\n<ul>\r\n\r\n<li>People who may need a later pickup than our group bus day tour pickups (which is usually around 8:30AM)</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Business people who are working on team building</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Families with small children, who may not want to visit wineries or stay on the bus tour</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Couples who want a private tour for themselves (perhaps make reservations at a restaurant and ride the skywheel on Clifton Hill)</li>\r\n\r\n<li>People who want to stay at the Falls for the entire day and visit attractions that are not on the bus tour (perhaps visit the Casino or the Wax </li>\r\n<li>Museum or Haunted House in Clifton Hill)</li>\r\n\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Booking is fast, safe and easy, once you have booking a ToNiagaraTours representative will email you and create a tentative itinerary with pickup/dropoff details as well as any attractions you would like to visit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will have a driver and 7 passenger tour vehicle for upto 9.5 hours.  To make your trip planning easier we offer tour add-ons like Helicopter Tour tickets, Hornblower Boat Cruise tickets and Sheraton Fallsview Restaurant Buffet.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"notes\">Please 