(22, 'Niagara Falls,Airplane Tours', 'Niagara Air Tours', 'Canada', 'Toronto to Niagara Falls Air Taxi Flight', 'toronto-to-niagara-falls-air-taxi-flight', ' ', 'Toronto To Niagara Falls Air Taxi Flight | Niagara Falls Tour', 'Toronto To Niagara Falls Air Taxi Flight | Niagara Falls Tour', 'Daily departures from Billy Bishop Airport, Toronto. Arrive in Niagara Falls like a VIP. Find out about luggage restrictions, ticket price, refund & cancellation policy. ', '<h3 class=\"heading3\"><p>Air Taxi Flight: Toronto to Niagara Falls</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Planning to travel to Niagara Falls?&nbsp; Skip the busy traffic and take an air taxi instead.</p>\r\n<p>Simply let us know when you would like to travel to Niagara Falls.&nbsp; Flights leave from the Billy Bishop Airport and a vehicle will be waiting to escort you to your Niagara Hotel (or other destination).<br></p>\r\n</h3>\r\n<div class=\"m_txt\"><p>This is a great way to save time and it cheaper than a private jet!</p>\r\n\r\n          </div>', 'Niagara Falls', ' ', '3', ' ', ' ', 'CA', '2 People (min)', 499, '- Each way for 2 Passengers', '', '3 People (min)', 749, '- Each way for 3 Passengers', ' ', 0, '', ' ', 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '<div>You will be contacted approximately 24 hours day before your flight with instructions where to go when you arrive at Billy Bishop Airport.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>2 Passenger minimum, call Niagara Falls Tour to arrange single passenger flights.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Transportation is not provided to:&nbsp; Billy Bishop Airport - 2 Eireann Quay, Toronto, ON M5V 1A1</div>\r\n', 'Once the trip is booked and confirmed <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">NO REFUNDS</span> will be provided unless your tour is cancelled due to poor weather conditions.', '<div class=\"txt\">\r\n                  <strong>When I arrive at Billy Bishop Airport, where do I go?</strong>\r\n<p>You will be contacted the day before your flight with instructions where to go when you arrive at Billy Bishop Airport.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>What happens when I land at St. Catharines/Niagara District Airport?</strong>\r\n<p>You will be picked up at the airport and driven to your hotel or destination, let the driver know when you would like to be picked up and he/she will pick you up and drive you back to the airport.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"read-more2\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Are there any weight/height restrictions for the plane?</strong>\r\n<p>If you can fit on standard airplane seat, you can will be able to fit onto the airplane. There are no height restrictions.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>Can infants/children take this tour?</strong>\r\n<p>Yes, infants and children and ride on the airplane.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>Do I need a passport?</strong>\r\n<p>A passport is not necessary.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>How many people does the plane seat?</strong>\r\n<p>The airplane sits 3 people (everybody gets a window seat)</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>How safe are small aircraft?</strong>\r\n<p>All airplanes are licensed by Transport Canada and subject to rigorous safety inspections</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>Do you fly in the winter?</strong>\r\n<p>Yes, Fall and Winter in the Niagara Region is beautiful.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>What happens if there is bad weather and you cannot fly?</strong>\r\n<p>If your flight is cancelled due to bad weather we will reschedule when possible, if not we will provide a full reimbursement.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>What is your cancellation policy?</strong>\r\n<p>Other than weather or operator cancellations, if the trip is cancelled for any other reason NO REFUND will be issued.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n              \r\n                  </div>', '<div class=\"txt\"><p>You will be contacted approximately 24 hours day before your flight with instructions where to go when you arrive at Billy Bishop Airport.</p>\r\n<p>Please print your ticket voucher and dress appropriately for the weather and remember to bring your camera.</p></div>', '20180820064719_555.jpg', '20180820064627_107.jpg', '', 'asd', 5, 1, 68, 19, '2018-08-20 18:46:27'),
(23, 'Niagara Falls,Airplane Tours', 'Niagara Air Tours', 'Canada', 'Niagara Falls to Toronto Air Taxi Flight', 'niagara-falls-to-toronto-air-taxi-flight', ' ', 'Niagara Falls To Toronto Air Taxi Flight | Niagara Falls Tour', ' ', 'Affordable air taxi flights to Toronto. Skip traffic jams, return to Torontoby airplane after your Niagara Falls tour. View Niagara region one last time from the skies!', '<h3 class=\"heading3\"><p>Air Taxi:&nbsp; Take a Quick Flight from Niagara Falls to Toronto</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"m_txt\">\r\n          <h3 class=\"heading3\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><p>Travelling from Niagara Falls to Toronto can be quick and easy with an Air Taxi.&nbsp; Skip the busy traffic and take an air taxi instead.</p>\r\n<p>Simply let us know when you would like to travel to Toronto and we will get you there quick, easy and&nbsp; cheaper than a private jet!</p>\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n          </div>', 'Niagara Falls', ' ', '0', '', '', 'CA', '2 People (min)', 499, ' - Each way for 2 Passengers', '', '3 People (min)', 749, ' - Each way for 3 Passengers', ' ', 0, ' ', ' ', 0, ' ', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Once the trip is booked and confirmed&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">NO REFUNDS</span>&nbsp;will be provided unless your tour is cancelled due to poor weather conditions.&nbsp;', '<div class=\"txt\">\r\n                  <strong>When I arrive at Billy Bishop Airport, where do I go?</strong>\r\n<p>You will be contacted the day before your flight with instructions where to go when you arrive at Billy Bishop Airport.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>What happens when I land at St. Catharines/Niagara District Airport?</strong>\r\n<p>You will be picked up at the airport and driven to your hotel or destination, let the driver know when you would like to be picked up and he/she will pick you up and drive you back to the airport.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>Are there any weight/height restrictions for the plane?</strong>\r\n<p>If you can fit on standard airplane seat, you can will be able to fit onto the airplane. There are no height restrictions.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"read-more2\">\r\n<strong>Can infants/children take this tour?</strong>\r\n<p>Yes, infants and children and ride on the airplane.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>Do I need a passport?</strong>\r\n<p>A passport is not necessary.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>How many people does the plane seat?</strong>\r\n<p>The airplane sits 3 people (everybody gets a window seat)</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>How safe are small aircraft?</strong>\r\n<p>All airplanes are licensed by Transport Canada and subject to rigorous safety inspections</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>Do you fly in the winter?</strong>\r\n<p>Yes, Fall and Winter in the Niagara Region is beautiful.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>What happens if there is bad weather and you cannot fly?</strong>\r\n<p>If your flight is cancelled due to bad weather we will reschedule when possible, if not we will provide a full reimbursement.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>What is your cancellation policy?</strong>\r\n<p>Other than weather or operator cancellations, if the trip is cancelled for any other reason NO REFUND will be issued.</p>\r\n\r\n      </div>            \r\n                  </div>', '', '20180820071311_419.jpg', '20180820071311_318.jpg', '', 'asd', 5, 1, 17, 20, '2018-08-20 19:13:11'),
(24, 'Niagara Falls', 'Family Tours,History & Culture,Sightseeing tours', 'Canada', 'Oakville To Niagara Falls Day Tour', 'oakville-to-niagara-falls-day-tour', ' ', 'Oakville to Niagara Falls Day Tour | Book Online | Niagara Falls Tour', 'Oakville to Niagara Falls Day Tour | Book Online | Niagara Falls Tour', 'Spend a day in Niagara Falls, take a scenic drive along the Niagara River, visit its many attractions. We take you to Niagara-on-the-Lake too! Read more. Book your ticket!', '<h3 class=\"heading3\"><p>Niagara Falls:  Visit The Most Famous Waterfalls In The World. We Run Day Tours Everyday.</p>\r\n\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"m_txt\">\r\n          <p>Not only is Niagara Falls one of the most breathtaking Wonders of the World, there are many more attractions to see and experience in Niagara.  Our Oakville to Niagara Falls Day Tour will shuttle you from Oakville to the Niagara Falls where you will board one of Niagara Falls most popular attractions the Hornblower Boat.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"read-more\">\r\n<p>Hop on board the Hornblower Boat Cruise (formerly known as the Maid of the Mist) get an up-close and personal view of the Great Niagara Falls (they will supply you with a rain poncho to keep you dry).  This is a unique photography opportunity and fun for the entire family!</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>For those who order the Lunch Buffet Add On, you will be taken to the Penthouse Level of the the Sheraton Fallsview Restaurant where you will be treated to a sumptuous meal with a stunning view overlooking the Niagara Falls.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>The tour then travels to Niagara-on-the-Lake. This quaint Victorian era town still is full of history and stunning architecture.  You will learn about the Battle of 1812 and participate in a wine (or grape juice) tasting at a local winery where you will learn how Niagara Region\'s World famous table and Ice wines are produced.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>After a full day of thrills and culture we will drop you back off safely in Oakville (unless you have purchased the Airport Dropoff Add On) with a camera full of memories.</p>\r\n\r\n </div>\r\n\r\n          </div>', 'Niagara Falls', '9.5 Hours', '12', '', '', 'CA', 'Price', 149, ' ', '', 'Seniors (Age 60+)', 139, ' ', 'Children (4-12 years)', 119, ' ', ' ', 0, ' ', '', '', '', '<ul class=\"inclu_list\">\r\n\r\n            <li>Hotel pickup and drop-off</li>\r\n<li>Wine Tasting At A Local Winery</li>\r\n<li>Niagara-On-The-Lake Tour</li>\r\n<li>Tour Guide</li>\r\n<li>Unlimited Free Bottled Water</li>\r\n<li>Wheelchair Access On Request*</li>\r\n<li>Free Lanyards</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n          <ul class=\"addon_list\">\r\n\r\n\r\n          </ul>', '<ul class=\"addon_list\">\r\n<li>Helicopter Ride (Add On)</li>\r\n<li>Buffet Lunch or Dinner (Add On)</li>\r\n<li>Airport Drop-Off (Add On)</li>\r\n<li>Next Day Pick Up (Add On)</li>\r\n</ul>', '<div class=\"txt\">\r\n                  <p>We pickup and drop-off from most hotels in Toronto, Airport area hotels and Mississauga Hotels*</p>\r\n<p>You will be requested to enter the pickup location in the last step of online booking. Your pick up time will be mentioned in the booking confirmation.</p>\r\n                  \r\n                  </div>', '<p>If a Day or Evening Bus Tour is cancelled less than 24 hours ahead&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">NO REFUND</span>&nbsp;will be provided.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"read-more2\">\r\n<ul class=\"cencel\">\r\n\r\n<li>You are responsible for arriving on time to your Niagara Falls Bus Tour. The pickup vehicle will usually wait for a few minutes; however, if you arrive late and miss the tour, NO REFUND will be provided. ToNiagara will specify your pickup time and location through email.</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>If, for any reason your tour is cancelled (due to inclement weather or other unforeseen circumstances), you will be notified as soon as possible and receive a&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">FULL REFUND</span>&nbsp;to your credit card or any other method of payment as applicable.</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Rescheduling your tour to another date is free of charge.</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>To switch your tour from day tour to evening tour, custom tour or vice versa, you will have to pay the difference in the tour fee. There are no additional processing fees. If you are switching to a less expensive tour, ToNiagara will refund the difference to your credit card.</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>In the rare event of a bus/vehicle breakdown all efforts will be made to continue the tour (another vehicle or vehicles may be sent to pick you up.)&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">NO REFUND</span>&nbsp;will be provided for any time lost on the tour or change in passenger vehicle. If the tour is cancelled due to bus/vehicle breakdown ToNiagara will be provide a full refund.</li>\r\n\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', '', '', '20180821094704_520.jpg', '20180821094704_482.jpg', '', 'asd', 5, 1, 16, 21, '2018-08-21 09:47:04');
