(33, 'Niagara Falls', 'Sightseeing tours', 'USA', 'Canadian Rainbow Illumination Evening Tour Niagara Falls, Ontario', 'canadian-rainbow-illumination-evening-tour-niagara-falls-ontario', 'Half Day Trip (4 Hours)', 'Evening Tour Of Niagara Falls Canada From Niagara Falls USA | Niagara Falls Tour', 'Evening Tour Of Niagara Falls Canada From Niagara Falls USA | Niagara Falls Tour', 'Four-hour tour of Niagara Falls Canada, includes Hornblower Boat Cruise, Floral Clock and more! Free pickup/dropoff from Niagara Falls USA hotels.', '<div class=\"m_txt\">\r\n<h3 class=\"heading3\">Canadian Rainbow Illumination Evening Bus Tour</h3>\r\n<p>Come and see the Niagara Falls lit up in the Evening on a Daily Illumination Evening Bus Tour. </p>\r\n<div class=\"read-more\">\r\n<p>Bring your passport and spend a day on the Canadian Side of Niagara Falls!</p>\r\n<p>This 4 hour tour will take you to all the popular attractions on the Canadian side of the Falls including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Hornblower Boat Cruise</li>\r\n<li>Niagara Whirlpool</li>\r\n<li>Floral Clock</li>\r\n<li>Souvenir shopping at Table Rock</li>\r\n<li>Much more!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Niagara Falls', '4 Hours', '0', '', '', 'US', 'Price', 104.95, ' ', '', ' ', 0, ' ', 'Children (5-12 years)', 74.95, ' ', 'Infants (0-4 years)', 0, ' Free', '', '', '', '<ul class=\"inclu_list\">\r\n<li>Hornblower Boat Cruise</li>\r\n<li>Escalation up the Skylon Tower for a bird\'s eye view of the Niagara Falls</li>\r\n<li>FREE return pass to go back and visit the Skylon Tower on your own</li>\r\n<li>Guided Tour of Niagara Falls, Ontario and surrounding region with full licensed guide/driver</li>\r\n</ul>', '', '<p>Complimentary Pickup from most downtown Niagara Falls USA hotels (you must contact the number provided on your ticket at least 24 hours before your tour and provide your pickup destination).</p>\r\n<p>You must present a printed copy of your electronic voucher to your guide at time of boarding</p>\r\n<p>Border crossing documents such as Passport and/or Visa required for cross-border tours</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"heading4\">Departure Times:</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"cencel\">\r\n<li>AMERICAN DEPARTURES: 5PM(TOUR START TIME)</li>\r\n<li>BUFFALO DEPARTURES: 5PM(TOUR START TIME)</li>\r\n<li>CANADIAN DEPARTURES:  5PM (TOUR START TIME)</li>\r\n</ul>', '<div class=\"txt\">\r\n<p>A full refund issued by ToNiagara if your tour is cancelled at least 24 hours before scheduled tour departure (this includes any issue arising at the U.S.A/Canada Border). <strong>NO REFUND</strong> will be issued if the tour is cancelled less than 24 hours before scheduled tour departure time.</p>\r\n</div>', '<strong>What type of documentation do I need for crossing the border on my tour?</strong>\r\n<p>United States and Canadian citizens ages 16 and older must present one of the following travel documents at the border:</p>\r\n<ul class=\"cencel\">\r\n<li>Valid U.S. or Canadian Passport</li>\r\n<li>Enhanced Driver\'s License (EDL)</li>\r\n<li>U.S. Passport Card</li>\r\n<li>Trusted Traveler Program Card</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"read-more2\">\r\n<p>United States and Canadian citizens under the age of 16, or under the age of 19 traveling with a school, religious or other youth group, must present one of the following travel documents at the border:</p>\r\n<ul class=\"cencel\">\r\n<li>Original or certified copy of birth certificate</li>\r\n<li>Naturalization Certificate</li>\r\n<li>Consular report of birth abroad</li>\r\n<li>Canadian Citizenship Card</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Lawful Permanent Residents of the United States must present a Permanent Resident Card (\"Green Card\", INS Form I-1551) at the border.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Residents of nations other than the United States and Canada may require a Canadian Visa along with their passport to enter Canada. Contact your national consulate before leaving home. International visitors will require passports to cross the border. Citizens of some countries may require a Canadian Visa as well. Be sure to check with our staff when booking your tour.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For the most up-to-date border crossing information, please access the following website: <a href=\"https://www.cbp.gov/\" target=\"_blank\">www.cbp.gov</a> (Subject to Change)</p>\r\n\r\n<strong>Where does my tour depart from?</strong>\r\n<p>There are multiple pickup points on both sides of the border, all within walking or driving distance from most hotels. We will provide directions to your departure point when you confirm  your tour.</p>\r\n\r\n<strong>Do I need to wait until I arrive at Niagara Falls to book my tour?</strong>\r\n<p>Due to the popularity of our tours, we recommend that you reserve your seats as soon as possible to guard against the possibility of a sell-out.</p>\r\n\r\n<strong>What type of clothing is recommended for the tour?</strong>\r\n<p>Comfortable walking shoes or sneakers are recommended. It is always a few degrees cooler near the water, so a jacket or sweater is also a good idea for cooler temperatures.</p>\r\n\r\n<strong>Do I need to bring money on tour with me?</strong>\r\n<p>The price of your tour includes all attraction and parking fees. You may want to bring some spending money or a credit card with you as you will be given the opportunity to purchase snacks or souvenirs. Tipping your tour guide is at your discretion.\r\n</p>\r\n<strong>Do you pickup from Buffalo?</strong>\r\n<p>Yes, we pick-up from any downtown or airport hotel in Buffalo for our tours.  There is an additional $40 round trip fee per party for these pickups, you can discuss when you confirm your tour.</p>\r\n\r\n<strong>Are meals included?</strong>\r\n<p>No, meals are not provided.  Breaks will be given throughout the tour in order for guests to purchase something to eat on their own.</p>\r\n</div>', '<div class=\"m_txt\">\r\n<h2 class=\"heading4\">Other information</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li> Tour itinerary is subject to change without notice</li>\r\n<li> Cameras and camcorders are welcome and encouraged!</li>\r\n<li> Comfortable clothing and shoes recommended</li>\r\n<li> Border crossing documents such as Passport and/or Visa required for cross-border tours</li>\r\n<li> Collapsable wheelchairs permitted with 24 hour advance notice</li>\r\n<li> MUST confirm 24-hours in advance</li>\r\n<li> No refunds will be made with less than 48 hour notice or the lack of border crossing documentation (if required for tour)</li>\r\n<li> Children 0-4 are FREE and considered lap children, thus NO seat will be reserved</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', '20180821115657_533.jpg', '20180821115657_655.jpg', '', '236556', 5, 1, 40, 30, '2018-08-21 11:56:57'),
(34, 'Niagara Falls,Niagara Falls Boat Tours', '', 'USA', 'Lewiston, NY Whirlpool Boat Tour â€“ Wet Jet Ride', 'lewiston-ny-whirlpool-boat-tour-wet-jet-ride', '(An Exciting Ride Down the Niagara River Rapids)', 'Whirlpool Jet Boat Tour â€“ Wet Ride, Lewiston NY | Niagara Falls Tour', 'Whirlpool Jet Boat Tour â€“ Wet Ride, Lewiston NY | Niagara Falls Tour', 'Take an open jet boat ride down the Niagara River Rapids. Tour departs from Lewiston, NY. Thrilling wet ride. Book your tickets online now!', '<h3 class=\"heading3\">White Water Rapids Adventure of a Lifetime!</h3>\r\n<div class=\"m_txt\">\r\n<p>This tour is a 45 minute non-stop adventure that will provide with fun memories that will last a lifetime!<br></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Experienced Whirlpool Jet Boat tour operators will take you up the Niagara River for a white water adventure.</p>\r\n<div class=\"read-more\">\r\n<p>You can easily register online by selecting the Green \"Book This Tour\" button.&nbsp; All participants must sign a participation agreement and attend a mandatory safety orientation before departing on the tour.&nbsp;<br></p>\r\n<p><strong>Wet Jet Boat Option (change of clothing highly recommended)</strong></p>\r\n          \r\n\r\n<table class=\"tbl_wet_jet\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n\r\n<tbody>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n\r\n<th>Lewiston, NY Departure Times</th>\r\n\r\n<th>May 18 â€“ May 24<br>\r\n<small>(Saturday and Sunday ONLY)</small></th>\r\n\r\n<th>May 25 â€“ June 29</th>\r\n\r\n<th>June 30 â€“ Sept. 3</th>\r\n\r\n<th>Sept. 4 â€“ Sept. 16</th>\r\n\r\n<th>Sept. 16 â€“ Sept. 30<br>\r\n<small>(Saturday and Sunday ONLY)</small></th>\r\n\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n\r\n<td><strong>Wet Jet Boat</strong><br>\r\nComplete change of<br>\r\nclothing needed</td>\r\n\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1:00 PM</td>\r\n\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1:00 PM<br>\r\n3:00 PM</td>\r\n\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">11:00 AM<br>\r\n1:00 PM<br>\r\n2:00 PM<br>\r\n3:00 PM</td>\r\n\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1:00 PM</td>\r\n\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1:00 PM</td>\r\n\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n</tbody>\r\n\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Niagara Falls', '0', '0', '', '', 'US', 'Price', 67, ' ', '', ' ', 0, ' ', 'Children (6-12 years)', 45, ' ', ' ', 0, ' ', '', '', '', '<ul class=\"inclu_list\">\r\n<li>Ponchos</li>\r\n<li>Water shoes</li>\r\n<li>Life jackets</li>\r\n<li>Free changing rooms</li>\r\n<li>Locker for valuables</li>\r\n</ul>', '', '', '<div class=\"txt\">\r\n                  <p>A full (100%) refund will be provided by Niagara Falls Tu for any cancellation request received at least 48 hours before the scheduled departure time. Any cancellation done within 48 hours of the scheduled departure time will receive <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">NO REFUND</span>.</p>\r\n                  </div>', '<strong>How can I stay Dry on this trip?</strong>\r\n<p>Take the Jet Dome tour where you do the same tour but in a covered boat instead of the open-top jet boat</p>\r\n<strong>Can seniors take this trip?</strong>\r\n<p>There is no age limit, though there is a height limit (you must be at least 44 inches tall or 3 feet 4 inches). You must be of good health, free of heart, neck or back issues and not pregnant.</p>\r\n<div class=\"read-more2\">\r\n<strong>How is seating arranged?</strong>\r\n<p>Seating is first come, first served and cannot be reserved. Young children (under 10 must sit towards the back of the boat)</p>\r\n<strong>How long is the trip?</strong>\r\n<p>Trips departing from Niagara-on-the-Lake are 60 minutes (round trip) while tours departing from Niagara Falls ON and Lewiston NY are 45 minutes (round trip). This time difference is because of the locations\' proximity to the Niagara Gorge. All 3 departures spend the same amount of time in the rapids!</p> \r\n<strong>Where does the boat go?</strong>\r\n<p>From either departure point, we travel upriver (south) and into the Niagara Gorge. Once in the gorge, 175 ft walls ascend from above the water line. The boat makes its way into the famous whirlpool and then we head back on down (north) through Devil\'s Hole Rapids. You return to the same location from which you boarded as our tour is a round trip excursion.</p>\r\n<strong>How many people does the boat hold?</strong>\r\n<p>There are 8 boats in the fleet. The Jet Dome holds 40 passengers. The Wet Jet boats hold 48 passengers each and two hold 54 passengers.</p>\r\n</div>', '<h2 class=\"heading4\">Boats</h2>\r\n<div class=\"txt\">\r\n                  <p>8 Jet Boats. These boats use a triple turbo diesel water jet system for both propulsion and steering. They are custom built with passenger safety as the most important feature.</p>                  \r\n                  </div>\r\n<h2 class=\"heading4\">Address (Departure Location)</h2>\r\n<div class=\"txt\">\r\n<p>Lewiston, NY Departure Location<br>\r\n115 South Water Street, Lewiston, NY  14092</p>        \r\n                  </div>\r\n<h2 class=\"heading4\">Printed Voucher</h2>\r\n<div class=\"txt\">\r\n<p>A Printed voucher of your booking confirmation should be presented to Whirlpool Jet Boat Tours staff upon arrival.</p>        \r\n                  </div>', '20180821124308_954.jpg', '20180821124308_494.jpg', '', '235879', 5, 1, 28, 31, '2018-08-21 12:43:08'),
(35, 'Niagara Falls', 'Wine Tours', 'Canada', 'Wine and Dine Private Tour Upto 6 Passengers', 'wine-and-dine-private-tour-upto-6-passengers', '(Your Perfect Wine Tasting Adventure)', 'Niagara Wine And Dine Private Tour â€“ Upto 6 People | Niagara Falls Tour', 'Niagara Wine And Dine Private Tour â€“ Upto 6 People | Niagara Falls Tour', 'Your perfect wine tasting adventure! Spend 6 heavenly hours visiting wineries, tasting wines and cider. Take a tour at one winery. Enjoy lunch at a winery restaurant!', '<h3 class=\"heading3\"><p>Take a Truly Unique Niagara-on-the-Lake Winery Tour</p>\r\n\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"m_txt\">\r\n<p><strong>Private Winery Excursion upto 6 passengers</strong></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Our Wine and Dine Private Tour allows you to travel around Niagara-on-the-Lake in your own luxury vehicle. Savor the sights and wines of Niagara-on-the-Lake with the perfect winery excursion through the beautiful Niagara regions.\r\nYour Wine and Dine Private Tour begins with pickup from your Niagara Falls or Niagara-on-the-Lake Hotels and B&amp;Bs. We then travel to Konzlemann Estate Winery for the \"Grand Wine Crafting Tour\".</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"read-more\">\r\n<p>The second stop visits either the Caroline Cellars or the Riverbend Inn and Vineyard (depending on availability) where lunch will be served (see the Menu here) and partake in a wine tasting.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>After a delicious lunch we will continue to 3 more award winning Wineries listed below (wineries are selected according to availability for tastings) (3-4 tastings per winery) at any the wineries below and then you will be dropped off back at your hotel or B&amp;B.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Caroline Cellars</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Trius Winery and Restaurant</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Peller Estates</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Lakeview Wine Co.</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Colaneri Estate Winery</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Hare Winery</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Riverview Cellars</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Palatine Hills Estate Winery</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"book_tour_big\"><a href=\"#\">I\'m Ready to Book a Private Wine and Dine Tour with Lunch </a></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Niagara Falls', '6 Hours', '0', 'Daily, 8AM to 9PM', '', 'CA', 'Price', 899.99, ' ', '', ' ', 0, ' ', 'Children (6-12 years)', 0, 'Free', ' ', 0, ' ', '', '', '', '<ul class=\"inclu_list\">\r\n\r\n    <li>Free pickup/dropoff from Niagara Falls and Niagara-on-the-Lake Hotels</li>\r\n\r\n    <li>1 Hour Wine Tour and tasting at Konzelmann Estate Winery</li>\r\n\r\n    <li>5 Wine tastings in total from various wineries in the region</li>\r\n\r\n    <li>Complimentary lunch</li>\r\n\r\n  </ul>', '<ul class=\"inclu_list2\">\r\n\r\n\r\n     <li>Visit to Chocolate FX Chocolate Factory, sample chocolate and enjoy and learn about chocolate making. $7.50 per person +tax</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n     <li>Cheese Please: $12.50 per person + tax</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n  </ul>', '<div class=\"txt\">\r\n                  <p>Pickup &amp; Drop-Off from Niagara Falls and Niagara-on-the-Lake Hotels and B&amp;B\'s </p>                  \r\n                  </div>', '<div class=\"txt\">\r\n                  <p>To change/cancel a Niagara Winery Bus Tour date please call or email ToNiagara. Customers will receive a FULL REFUND if they call at least 48 hours ahead to cancel.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If the Tour is cancelled less than 48 hours ahead NO REFUND will be provided.</p>\r\n<div class=\"read-more2\">\r\n<ul class=\"cencel\">\r\n\r\n<li>You are responsible for arriving on time to your Niagara Winery Tour. The pickup vehicle will usually wait for a few minutes; however, if you arrive late and miss the tour, NO REFUND will be provided. ToNiagara will specify your pickup time and location through email.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>If, for any reason your tour is cancelled (due to inclement weather or other unforeseen circumstances), you will be notified as soon as possible and receive a FULL REFUND to your credit card or any other method of payment as applicable.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Rescheduling your tour to another date is free of charge.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>To switch/edit your custom tour, you will have to pay the difference in the tour fee. There are no additional processing fees. If you are switching to a less expensive tour, ToNiagara will refund the difference to your credit card.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>In the rare event of a vehicle breakdown all efforts will be made to continue the tour (another vehicle or vehicles may be sent to pick you up.) NO REFUND will be provided for any time lost on the tour or change in passenger vehicle. If the tour is cancelled due to vehicle breakdown ToNiagara will be provide a full refund.</li>\r\n\r\n</ul>\r\n </div>\r\n\r\n                  </div>', '', '<h2 class=\"heading4\">Printed Voucher</h2>\r\n<div class=\"txt\">\r\n<p>Printed voucher of booking confirmation should be presented to the Tour Operator.</p>        \r\n                  </div>\r\n<h2 class=\"heading4\">How many people are on the tour?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"txt\">\r\n<p>This private tour uses a luxury 7 passenger vehicle.</p>        \r\n                  </div>', '20180821125716_689.jpg', '20180821125716_477.jpg', '', 'asd', 5, 1, 29, 32, '2018-08-21 12:57:16'),
(36, 'Niagara Falls', 'Wine Tours', 'Canada', 'Wine and Dine Private Tour â€“ Upto 4 Passengers', 'wine-and-dine-private-tour-upto-4-passengers', '(Your Perfect Wine Tasting Adventure)', 'Wine And Dine Private Niagara Tour â€“ Upto 4 Persons | Niagara Falls Tour', 'Wine And Dine Private Niagara Tour â€“ Upto 4 Persons | Niagara Falls Tour', 'Visit Niagara wineries, 6-hour tour. Lunch at a winery restaurant. Wine tastings at each winery, one winery tour. Learn how wine is made. Enjoy the fresh air of the countryside.', '<h3 class=\"heading3\"><p>Take a Truly Unique Niagara-on-the-Lake Winery Tour</p></h3>\r\n<div class=\"m_txt\">\r\n<strong>Private Winery Tour upto 4 passengers</strong>\r\n<p>Our Wine and Dine Private Tour allows you to travel around Niagara-on-the-Lake in your own classic London cab. Savor the sights and wines of Niagara-on-the-Lake with the perfect winery excursion through the beautiful Niagara regions.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"read-more\">\r\n<p>Your Wine and Dine Private Tour begins with pickup from your Niagara Falls or Niagara-on-the-Lake Hotels and B&amp;Bs. We then travel to Konzlemann Estate Winery for the \"Grand Wine Crafting Tour\".</p>\r\n<p>The second stop visits either the Caroline Cellars or the Riverbend Inn and Vineyard (depending on availability) where lunch will be served (see the Menu here) and partake in a wine tasting.</p>\r\n<p>After a delicious lunch we will continue to 3 more award winning Wineries listed below (wineries are selected according to availability for tastings) (3-4 tastings per winery) at any the wineries below and then you will be dropped off back at your hotel or B&amp;B</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Caroline Cellars</li>\r\n<li>Trius Winery and Restaurant</li>\r\n<li>Peller Estates</li>\r\n<li>Lakeview Wine Co.</li>\r\n<li>Colaneri Estate Winery</li>\r\n<li>Hare Winery</li>\r\n<li>Riverview Cellars</li>\r\n<li>Palatine Hills Estate Winery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"book_tour_big\"><a href=\"#\"