(39, 'Niagara Falls', '', 'Canada', 'Niagara Falls Whirlpool Boat Tour â€“ Wet Jet Ride', 'niagara-falls-whirlpool-boat-tour-wet-jet-ride', '(An Exciting Ride Down the Niagara River Rapids)', 'Niagara Whirlpool Jet Boat Tour â€“ Wet Ride | Niagara Falls Tour', ' ', 'Feel the adrenaline rush as the open jet boat speeds through the Niagara River Rapids. Enjoy the scenery, experience Niagaraâ€™s power as waves crashover you. Book now!', '<h3 class=\"heading3\">Have a Wet and Wild Adventure on a Whirlpool Jet Boat</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"m_txt\">\r\n<strong>Wet Jet Boat Option (change of clothing highly recommended)</strong>\r\n\r\n<p>Experience the most thrilling boat ride on the Niagara River! Let the experienced tour operators take you for the ride of your life along the Niagara River.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"read-more\">\r\n<p>Travel deep into the Niagara Gorge, passing through the famous Niagara Whirlpool and into the Devil\'s Hole Rapids. This is an exhilarating adventure, the memories will last a lifetime</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Register, sign a participation agreement and attend a mandatory safety orientation. You can click here: to fill out your participation agreement in advance.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"tbl_scroll\">\r\n          <table class=\"tbl_wet_jet\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n\r\n<tbody>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n\r\n<th>Niagara Falls Departure Times</th>\r\n\r\n<th>April 28 â€“ May 18</th>\r\n\r\n<th>May 19 â€“ June 22</th>\r\n\r\n<th>June 23 â€“ Sept. 3</th>\r\n\r\n<th>Sept. 4 â€“ Oct. 21</th>\r\n\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n\r\n<td><strong>Wet Jet Boat</strong><br>\r\nComplete change of<br>\r\nclothing needed</td>\r\n\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">3:00 PM</td>\r\n\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">3:00 PM</td>\r\n\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">12:00 PM<br>\r\n1:00 PM<br>\r\n2:00 PM<br>\r\n3:00 PM<br>\r\n4:00 PM</td>\r\n\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">3:00 PM</td>\r\n\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n</tbody>\r\n\r\n</tabl