(40, 'Niagara Falls', 'Wine Tours', 'Canada', 'Niagara-on-the-Lake Daily Wine, Cheese and Chocolate Tour', 'niagara-on-the-lake-daily-wine-cheese-and-chocolate-tour', '(5 Hour Afternoon Winery Tour with Cheese Pairing and Chocolate Factory Visit)', 'Niagara-on-the-Lake Wine, Cheese, Chocolate Tour| Niagara Falls Tour', ' ', 'Wine tasting and tour of one winery.Taste wine and cheese pairings at more wineries. End your 5-hour tour with a tour of a chocolate factory. Buy wines & chocolates!', '<h3 class=\"heading3\"><p>Spend a Day Exploring Niagara Wine Country</p></h3>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"m_txt\">\r\n          <p><strong>Afternoon Winery Tour and Tasting with Cheese and Chocolate Sampling</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This popular 5-hour afternoon tour is a less expensive and great way to learn about the Niagara region. Your tour begins at the Konzlemann Estate Winery for the \"Grand Wine Crafting Tour\" and includes an educated, structured wine tasting.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"read-more\">\r\n<p>We will visit three more wineries for tastings from the list below (wineries are selected according to availability), including a wine and cheese pairing at Reif Estate Winery.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\r\n<li>Caroline Cellars</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Trius Winery and Restaurant</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Peller Estates</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Lakeview Wine Co.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Colaneri Estate Winery</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Hare Winery</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Riverview Cellars</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Palatine Hills Estate Winery</li>\r\n\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Lastly, we stop at Chocolate Fx for a tour of this chocolate factory, get ready to taste the best chocolate in Ontario!</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>The tour ends with you being dropped off at your hotel or B&amp;B. For a more intimate winery experience take a custom winery tour. Click here for more details.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"book_tour_big\"><a href=\"#\">I\'m Ready to Book This Tour</a></div>', 'Niagara Falls', '5 Hours', '0', 'Daily, 8AM to 9PM', ' ', 'CA', 'Price