for any time lost on the tour or change in passenger vehicle. If the tour is cancelled due to vehicle breakdown ToNiagara will be provide a full refund.</li>\r\n\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n                  </div>', '', '<h2 class=\"heading4\">Printed Voucher</h2>\r\n<div class=\"txt\">\r\n<p>Printed voucher of booking confirmation <strong>MUST</strong> be presented to the Tour Operator.</p>        \r\n                  </div>\r\n<h2 class=\"heading4\">How many people are on the tour?</h2>\r\n<div class=\"txt\">\r\n<p>It depends on what season, however there are usually between 8 and 20 people on each Winery Tour.  Smaller tour groups are available in our private winery tours section.</p>        \r\n                  </div>', '20180821050316_707.jpg', '20180821050316_571.jpg', '', 'asd', 5, 1, 11, 35, '2018-08-21 17:03:16'),
(41, 'Niagara Falls', '', 'Canada', 'Group Wine Tour with Lunch', 'group-wine-tour-with-lunch', '', 'Group Wine Tour with Lunch Niagara, Ontario', 'Best Niagara Falls Sightseeing Tours, Tour Packages, Day Tour, Evening Tour, Small Group Custom Tour, Private Tour, Group Tours', 'Explore Niagara\'s wine country with a group wine tour with lunch included. Complimentary pickup and drop-off and wine tastings at 5 different popular wineries.', '<h3 class=\"heading3\">Niagara-on-the-Lake Group Wine Tour with Lunch</h3>\r\n<div class=\"m_txt\">\r\n<strong>Small Group Winery Bus Tour&nbsp;</strong>\r\n<p>Take a leisurely 5-hour tour around Niagara-on-the-Lake\'s rich wine region with our small group bus tour.&nbsp; On this winery tour you will visit 5 different wineries and have 3-4 wine tastings per winery.</p>\r\n<div class=\"read-more\">\r\n<p>Complimentary pickup from your Niagara Falls or Niagara-on-the-Lake Hotels and B&amp;Bs. We then travel to Konzlemann Estate Winery for the \"Grand Wine Crafting Tour\".</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The second stop visits either the Caroline Cellars (See Menu <a href=\"https://www.toniagara.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Caroline-Cellars-The-Farmhouse-Cafe-Group-Lunch.pdf\">here</a>) or the Riverbend Inn and Vineyard (see Menu <a href=\"https://www.toniagara.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Riverbend-grape-and-wine-Lunch.pdf\">here</a>) (depending on availability) where lunch will be served (Menus are subject to change without notice) and partake in a wine tasting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After a delicious lunch we will continue to 3 more award winning Wineries listed below (wineries are selected according to availability for tastings) (3-4 tastings per winery) at any the wineries below and then you will be dropped off back at your hotel or B&amp;B.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Caroline Cellars</li>\r\n<li>Trius Winery and Restaurant</li>\r\n<li>Peller Estates</li>\r\n<li>Lakeview Wine Co.</li>\r\n<li>Colaneri Estate Winery</li>\r\n<li>Hare Winery</li>\r\n<li>Riverview Cellars</li>\r\n<li>Palatine Hills Estate Winery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Included:</strong></p>\r\n<ul class=\"inclu_list2\">\r\n<li>Free pickup/dropoff from Niagara Falls and Niagara-on-the-Lake Hotels</li>\r\n<li>1 Hour Wine Tour and tasting at Konzelmann Estate Winery</li>\r\n<li>5 Wine tastings in total from various wineries in the region</li>\r\n<li>Complimentary lunch</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"xola-checkout xola-custom\" data-seller=\"591328906864eab4788b4593\" data-experience=\"5a81ad93332e75eb5e8b45b4\" data-version=\"2\">Book your Group Wine Tour with Lunch TODAY!</div>', 'Niagara Falls', '6 Hours', '0', '', '', 'CA', 'Price', 124.99, '', '', 'Seniors (Age 60+)', 0, '', 'Children (4-12 years)', 0, '', 'Infants (0-2 years)', 0, '', '', '', '', '<ul class=\"inclu_list\">\r\n  <li>Hornblower Cruise (seasonal)</li>\r\n  <li>Hotel pickup and drop-off</li>\r\n  <li>Wine Tasting At A Local Winery</li>\r\n  <li>Niagara-On-The-Lake Tour</li>\r\n  <li>Tour Guide</li>\r\n  <li>Unlimited Free Bottled Water</li>\r\n  <li>Wheelchair Access On Request*</li>\r\n  <li>Free Lanyards</li>\r\n  <li>Helicopter Ride (Add On)</li>\r\n  <li>Buffet Lunch or Dinner (Add On)</li>\r\n  <li>Airport Drop-Off (Add On)</li>\r\n  <li>Next Day Pick Up (Add On)</li>\r\n</ul>', '', 'Pickup &amp; Drop-Off from Niagara Falls and Niagara-on-the-Lake Hotels and B&amp;Bâ€™s', '<p>To change/cancel a Niagara Winery Bus Tour date please call or email ToNiagara. Customers will receive a FULL REFUND if they call at least 48 hours ahead to cancel.</p>\r\n<p>If the Tour is cancelled less than 48 hours ahead NO REFUND will be provided.</p>\r\n<div class=\"read-more2\">\r\n<ul class=\"cencel\">\r\n<li>You are responsible for arriving on time to your Niagara Winery Tour. The pickup vehicle will usually wait for a few minutes; however, if you arrive late and miss the tour, NO REFUND will be provided. ToNiagara will specify your pickup time and location through email.</li>\r\n<li>If, for any reason your tour is cancelled (due to inclement weather or other unforeseen circumstances), you will be notified as soon as possible and receive a FULL REFUND to your credit card or any other method of payment as applicable.</li>\r\n<li>Rescheduling your tour to another date is free of charge.</li>\r\n<li>To switch/edit your custom tour, you will have to pay the difference in the tour fee. There are no additional processing fees. If you are switching to a less expensive tour, ToNiagara will refund the difference to your credit card.</li>\r\n<li>In the rare event of a vehicle breakdown all efforts will be made to continue the tour (another vehicle or vehicles may be sent to pick you up.) NO REFUND will be provided for any time lost on the tour or change in passenger vehicle. If the tour is cancelled due to vehicle breakdown ToNiagara will be provide a full refund.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', '', '<h2 class=\"heading4\">Printed Voucher</h2>\r\n<p>Printed voucher of booking confirmation should be presented to the Tour Operator.</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"heading4\">How many people are on the tour?</h2>\r\n<p>This private tour uses a classic London Taxi Cab which can seat upto 4 people.</p>', '20181103051259_857.jpg', '20181103051259_852.jpg', '', 'a', 5, 1, 19, 39, '2018-09-03 17:29:10'),
(42, 'Niagara Falls', '', 'USA', 'Best Value Toronto to Niagara Falls Day Tour Without Boat Cruise Ride', 'best-value-toronto-to-niagara-falls-day-tour-without-boat-cruise-ride', '', 'Toronto To Niagara Falls Day Tour | Book Your Tour Now', 'Best Niagara Falls Sightseeing Tours, Tour Packages, Day Tour, Evening Tour, Small Group Custom Tour, Private Tour, Group Tours', 'Niagara Falls is One Of The Most Beautiful Places. We run Toronto to Niagara Falls Day Tour everyday. Learn more about the tour schedule &amp; itinerary.', '<h4>Cheapest Toronto to Niagara Falls Daily Bus Tour (Lunch and Hornblower Boat Cruise Not Included)</h4><div>Our low budget Toronto to Niagara Falls bus tour picks up from two convenient downtown Toronto Locations and takes you to the natural World wonder of Niagara Falls.</div><div></div><div>This tour is perfect for the solo traveler or families that would like to skip the Hornblower boat cruise but still see the magnificence of Niagara Falls.</div><div></div><div>We visit many of the popular tourist attractions including:</div><ul> 	<li>Niagara Falls</li> 	<li>Whirlpool Rapids</li> 	<li>Floral Clock</li> 	<li>Niagara-on-the-Lake</li> 	<li>Wine tasting at a local winery</li></ul><div class=\"itinerary_head\">Tour Itinerary</div>', 'Niagara Falls', '9.5 Hours', '203', '', '', 'US', 'Adults price', 99, '', '', 'Seniors (Age 60+)', 0, '', 'Children (4-12 years)', 0, '', 'Infants (0-2 years)', 0, '', '<p><br></p>', '', '', '<ul>  <li>Hornblower Cruise (seasonal)</li>  <li>Hotel pickup and drop-off</li>  <li>Wine Tasting At A Local Winery</li>  <li>Niagara-On-The-Lake Tour</li>  <li>Tour Guide</li>  <li>Unlimited Free Bottled Water</li>  <li>Wheelchair Access On Request*</li>  <li>Free Lanyards</li>  <li>Helicopter Ride (Add On)</li>  <li>Buffet Lunch or Dinner (Add On)</li>  <li>Airport Drop-Off (Add On)</li>  <li>Next Day Pick Up (Add On)</li></ul>', '', '<div>We pickup from 2 downtown Toronto locations:</div><div>Â </div><div>1.Â  The Hardrock Cafe 279 Yonge St, Toronto, ON M5B 1N8 (pickup between 8:20 and 8:45AM) or</div><div>Â </div><div>2.Â  Tim Horton\'s Coffee Shop 340 Front St W, Toronto, ON M5V 3W7 (pickup between 8:40 and 9:00AM)</div>', '<p>i.Â  Customer reservations can be cancelled upto 24 hours in advance of scheduled arrival without penalty; refunds will not be issued if customer cancels within 24 hours of scheduled departure</p><p>ii. In the case of tour operator cancellations a full refund will be issued to the customer by ToNiagara (if a subsequent date cannot be rescheduled)</p><p>iii. In the event of a refund, ToNiagara will reimburse the customer directly and remit the amount from the subsequent payment to Tour Operator</p>', '', '', '20180903053428_197.', '20180903053428_328.', '', 'a', 5, 0, 0, 38, '2018-09-03 17:34:28');
